2831799630
01:22:52.938 --> 01:22:55.640
I think it's a wrong argument to say that

3585545547
01:22:55.641 --> 01:22:58.937
if we were to issue new licences today,

1138436507
01:22:58.938 --> 01:23:01.747
that that would affect
the the energy crisis that we're

501561633
01:23:01.748 --> 01:23:04.356
facing because of
the situation in the Middle East.

1769863757
01:23:04.357 --> 01:23:06.994
And what we absolutely have to do is we

508022552
01:23:06.995 --> 01:23:08.750
absolutely have to make sure today

596222768
01:23:09.588 --> 01:23:13.340
that we deal with the with
