1646700181
01:23:13.341 --> 01:23:16.039
It was not our choice to
have this war in Iran.

1139243935
01:23:16.040 --> 01:23:17.445
We've not taken part in it.

3289969214
01:23:17.446 --> 01:23:21.691
We think it was a mistake
