213013496
01:23:33.934 --> 01:23:35.087
>> John Slinger thank.

459887328
01:23:35.088 --> 01:23:35.690
>> You, Mr.

2375784922
01:23:36.543 --> 01:23:36.993
Speaker.

3777985821
