1219583654
04:26:50.779 --> 04:26:53.186
the conflict goes on with
torture, sham trials,

1326430711
04:26:53.187 --> 04:26:55.294
executions all being used to try and beat

1169322986
04:26:55.295 --> 04:26:57.378
the Iranian people into submission.

2109173586
04:26:57.379 --> 04:26:59.793
And we're only getting so much information

1339272414
04:26:59.794 --> 04:27:02.332
