950751912
04:27:30.782 --> 04:27:33.476
In 2022, when Iran cracked down brutally

2721614064
04:27:33.477 --> 04:27:36.225
on the women Life and Freedom protest.

3155929426
04:27:36.226 --> 04:27:39.437
But of course, all of this is
