threats here at home in the UK.

1391823007
04:27:56.733 --> 04:27:59.937
In the last year alone,
the threat has only grown.

2264069146
04:27:59.938 --> 04:28:02.932
The chief rabbi has said
that the British Jews,

2858546363
04:28:02.933 --> 04:28:06.132
that British Jews and Iranian
dissidents here are facing

3455723539
04:28:06.133 --> 04:28:09.088
a sustained campaign of
violence and intimidation.

2357631027
04:28:09.089 --> 04:28:10.343
And we've all seen this.

2998496708
04:28:10.780 --> 04:28:13.036
We saw the ambulances
