We saw Jewish charities,
the Israeli embassy,

1441222563
04:28:23.634 --> 04:28:27.085
the Iranian media all targeted
and most horrifyingly of all,

2704287904
04:28:27.086 --> 04:28:29.194
we saw two Jews stabbed on the streets of

2348273035
04:28:29.195 --> 04:28:32.680
London simply because they were Jewish.

3682848384
04:28:32.682 --> 04:28:33.535
Now all of this.

3382486194
04:28:33.536 --> 04:28:36.082
The police and security experts suspect,

3970613658
04:28:36.083 --> 04:28:38.535
and there are ongoing investigations,

2805867442
04:28:38.536 --> 04:28:41.079
is the work of paid proxies
and criminal gangs

3100773648
04:28:41.080 --> 04:28:45.179
