associate with the IRGC,

559374567
04:29:35.192 --> 04:29:38.392
profess support for it,
sharing materials from it or

1720628178
04:29:38.393 --> 04:29:41.185
attend any meetings with
their representatives,

1805250037
04:29:41.186 --> 04:29:45.036
and this new power must require
all IRGC online material,

4161727847
04:29:45.037 --> 04:29:49.491
