355293019
04:30:38.292 --> 04:30:40.347
These must be identified and dismantled.

4244693353
04:30:40.348 --> 04:30:43.554
And thirdly, the government's
Protecting what matters strategy,

625483101
04:30:43.555 --> 04:30:46.113
which was extremely welcome
when it was announced,

19132026
04:30:46.114 --> 04:30:50.039
