full and implemented quickly.

2919086324
04:30:50.040 --> 04:30:53.142
Now I finish by saying this,
Madam Deputy Speaker,

501132390
04:30:53.779 --> 04:30:58.987
the Iranian regime is one of
the world's worst abuses of human rights.

3166033435
04:30:58.988 --> 04:31:01.737
It menaces our allies in the region with

3820154096
04:31:01.738 --> 04:31:04.235
