community here at home.

4032248945
04:31:10.487 --> 04:31:12.894
I do commend the government
for the seriousness

1049557976
04:31:12.894 --> 04:31:14.600
with which it treats this danger,

1324038672
04:31:15.790 --> 04:31:17.594
underlined by this new legislation.

3038748014
04:31:17.595 --> 04:31:21.736
Now we have to get on passed
these new laws and prescribe

4267010402
04:31:21.737 --> 04:31:24.394
the biggest state sponsor
of terrorism in the world.

3572774135
04:31:24.396 --> 04:31:28.092
It is time to prescribe
the IRGC a Stuart Anderson.

