2885351521
05:50:40.680 --> 05:50:42.885
research and development
and manufacturing.

1932315888
05:50:42.886 --> 05:50:46.146
And Madam Deputy Speaker, I look
forward to enabling and working

844146789
05:50:46.147 --> 05:50:49.356
with the Department and
