colleges were awarded to Portsmouth

1050875466
05:50:57.429 --> 05:51:00.489
or our surrounding area because
our city has the industrial,

3540483876
05:51:00.490 --> 05:51:02.796
heritage, skills
and base and defence experts

3057249575
05:51:02.797 --> 05:51:04.352
to play leading roles in this,

4282718978
05:51:04.353 --> 05:51:07.314
and I would like to explore
with the department how we can

2134634984
05:51:07.315 --> 05:51:09.922
access this opportunity
further and close this gap.

1338672082
05:51:09.923 --> 05:51:12.579
Portsmouth businesses do not
want special treatment.

4162199883
05:51:12.580 --> 05:51:15.036
Portsmouth people do not
want special treatment,

1783757387
05:51:15.036 --> 05:51:16.592
just a fair chance to survive.

703052438
05:51:16.593 --> 05:51:20.254
And as a proud naval city, Portsmouth
understands the sacrifices made by

2479820881
05:51:20.255 --> 05:51:23.715
our armed >> Forces veterans
and military families better than most.

2074673095
05:51:23.715 --> 05:51:25.971
We also understand
the enormous contribution

598682602
05:51:25.972 --> 05:51:28.078
made every day by the workers, engineers,

2474697555
05:51:28.079 --> 05:51:31.588
apprenticeships and small businesses
that help keep our country safe.

4276055703
05:51:31.589 --> 05:51:34.948
Because one of the greatest strengths
of Portsmouth is its people,

4079778689
05:51:34.950 --> 05:51:37.709
and the way the people from
all faiths and backgrounds

2963654911
05:51:37.710 --> 05:51:41.117
stand together at a time when
many faiths and communities have

3525877701
05:51:41.118 --> 05:51:43.826
felt under attack or targeted
by division and hatred.

92623174
05:51:43.827 --> 05:51:46.817
We must continue to work
together to protect tolerance,

2859145509
05:51:46.818 --> 05:51:51.522
respect and community cohesion
across my city and this country.

1161356170
05:51:51.523 --> 05:51:55.034
So, Madam Deputy Speaker, as we begin
this new session of Parliament,

3705448294
05:51:55.035 --> 05:51:57.292
my focus remains solidly
where it has always

2105771096
05:51:57.293 --> 05:51:59.298
been working hard for Portsmouth North,

3323117473
05:51:59.299 --> 05:52:02.006
championing local businesses
and making sure our city

2673303561
05:52:02.007 --> 05:52:04.616
plays a full and leading
role in building a fairer,

3969757505
05:52:05.868 --> 05:52:07.923
stronger and more secure United Kingdom.

2315494300
05:52:07.924 --> 05:52:09.579
And as the Member of Parliament,

1873100797
05:52:09.580 --> 05:52:12.189
I am going to pull every
lever possible within this

3318559624
05:52:12.190 --> 05:52:15.301
government to ensure that these
are not just words on a page,

3503477414
05:52:15.302 --> 05:52:17.320
but tangible actions.

108784830
05:52:17.321 --> 05:52:18.072
>> Hear, hear.

3116018829
05:52:18.073 --> 05:52:20.468
>> Shockat Adam thank you, Madam.

2742733376
05:52:20.469 --> 05:52:21.421
>> Deputy Speaker.

3736939385
05:52:21.422 --> 05:52:24.674
It's a pleasure to follow
on from the very powerful

2751064662
05:52:24.675 --> 05:52:27.321
speech by the Member for Portsmouth North.

2074290019
05:52:27.322 --> 05:52:29.719
I want to use my time today to address

1075315509
05:52:29.720 --> 05:52:32.419
the issues that matter to the defence of

3703034237
05:52:32.420 --> 05:52:34.376
our country and its future from a very

1665073666
05:52:34.863 --> 05:52:36.717
domestic perspective and touch upon,

1869109390
05:52:36.718 --> 05:52:40.533
if I have time on the historical
waste in the defence industry.

1019566967
05:52:41.868 --> 05:52:45.328
Following on from what the former
Health Secretary said, that sadly,

3711232319
05:52:45.329 --> 05:52:49.426
around 50% of young people today say
they will not defend our country.

3209006668
05:52:49.872 --> 05:52:51.126
Now the question is why?

1568343475
05:52:51.126 --> 05:52:52.382
Is it because we do not?

1084690665
05:52:52.867 --> 05:52:54.825
Is it because we do not build a strong

3781277297
05:52:54.826 --> 05:52:57.371
country by making poor people poorer,

3304330658
05:52:57.372 --> 05:53:01.822
and we do not build a strong
army from an unhealthy,

2294930302
05:53:01.823 --> 05:53:04.470
undereducated, economically
broken population?

1790535390
05:53:04.471 --> 05:53:07.425
The two things are not in competition.

2325450933
05:53:07.426 --> 05:53:08.428
They are connected.

3126840417
05:53:08.826 --> 05:53:11.134
There is an argument
that has been made today

1291331354
05:53:11.135 --> 05:53:13.823
that we must sacrifice
welfare for warfare,

835282072
05:53:13.825 --> 05:53:16.727
that strip the safety net
to fund the military.

4022899963
05:53:16.728 --> 05:53:20.375
But my argument is this
the things that make people feel

142576137
05:53:20.863 --> 05:53:25.421
safe at home are exactly what
makes us worth defending.

3683997710
05:53:25.422 --> 05:53:27.427
We talk endlessly about threats abroad,

917949651
05:53:27.428 --> 05:53:30.376
but the things that lead to
instability like poverty,

2532838283
05:53:30.869 --> 05:53:35.518
inequality, failed public services,
communities left behind.

771339214
05:53:35.519 --> 05:53:36.622
Those are right here.

657170029
05:53:36.623 --> 05:53:43.620
Just this weekend, on Saturday at
the allegedly Unite the Kingdom march,

2848715353
05:53:43.621 --> 05:53:47.571
we saw rhetoric and vile Islamophobic
shouts of organisers and speakers

2817737897
05:53:47.572 --> 05:53:51.525
on stage calling for Muslims to
be deported from this country

2025760044
05:53:51.526 --> 05:53:55.874
and calling for Muslims from deported
from this place where we sit,

1418608839
05:53:55.875 --> 05:53:59.221
members of either party across
the board were openly told

3193865027
05:53:59.222 --> 05:54:02.485
to go back home despite being
born and brought up here.

1379780701
05:54:02.486 --> 05:54:05.446
These are the things that are
going to destroy our nation.

354151681
05:54:05.447 --> 05:54:08.427
These are the things that we
really need to worry about.

598626601
05:54:08.827 --> 05:54:11.636
And also, before I proceed
to address the other issues,

2618396724
05:54:11.637 --> 05:54:14.618
I would like to also
highlight the colossal waste

1419964623
05:54:14.619 --> 05:54:16.573
of money in previous defence projects,

1756715063
05:54:16.867 --> 05:54:21.321
because many people jump on the fact
that defence must be spent again,

2853640487
05:54:21.322 --> 05:54:24.371
as I mentioned at the at
the sacrifice of our welfare,

4010774969
05:54:24.372 --> 05:54:26.329
because that is such a waste of money.

20895270
05:54:26.330 --> 05:54:30.774
So I would just like to
mention the Ajax armoured

545475093
05:54:30.775 --> 05:54:32.779
vehicle programme costing Â£5.5 billion.

3683991904
05:54:32.780 --> 05:54:37.479
It's still not ready and is
running over a decade late.

800483427
05:54:37.480 --> 05:54:38.834
The Bowman Radio cost Â£2.5

2983128091
05:54:38.835 --> 05:54:42.224
billion 25 years late
and still doesn't work properly,

697177362
05:54:42.225 --> 05:54:46.136
and the type 45 daring
class destroyers are Â£1.5

1612322722
05:54:46.137 --> 05:54:48.394
billion over Budget
and the majority are now

4162805921
05:54:50.871 --> 05:54:53.129
maintained in a dock
less than 15 years old.

742863231
05:54:53.130 --> 05:54:56.391
So I would like to speak about
the economy and more specifically

3202469633
05:54:56.392 --> 05:54:58.549
with the businesses that sit at its heart.

330834018
05:54:58.550 --> 05:55:01.157
Small and medium sized
enterprises are the backbone

3257087929
05:55:01.158 --> 05:55:03.363
Madam Deputy Speaker
of British prosperity.

2232907218
05:55:04.872 --> 05:55:06.777
In my constituency of Leicester South

2866094178
05:55:06.778 --> 05:55:09.084
and as in constituencies
across this country,

1887566390
05:55:09.085 --> 05:55:10.673
the employers, the innovators,

3481317751
05:55:10.674 --> 05:55:13.632
the anchor institutions of our
high streets and industrial

3761419276
05:55:13.633 --> 05:55:16.876
estates are being hammered
with increased cost of living,

1245035367
05:55:16.876 --> 05:55:19.922
whether that's energy
and business rates, rises,

1928773861
05:55:19.923 --> 05:55:24.621
increased costs to staffing budgets
or national insurance contributions.

3290136140
05:55:24.622 --> 05:55:28.081
Last year alone, the OBR found that
National Insurance contributions

366666819
05:55:28.082 --> 05:55:30.540
caused a 2% hike in payroll
costs for employers.

4033289254
05:55:30.541 --> 05:55:33.376
While CEOs confidence has fallen more in

329953605
05:55:33.378 --> 05:55:35.371
recent years than during a pandemic.

1223635417
05:55:35.372 --> 05:55:38.779
When this government talks
a defence and it's spending.

3419636421
05:55:38.780 --> 05:55:40.436
It must come from the bottom up.

3507057195
05:55:40.437 --> 05:55:43.773
We must be investing in its future
rather than piling costs onto

2634403024
05:55:43.774 --> 05:55:46.933
our own businesses and thus
allowing corporations to run riot.

208373716
05:55:46.934 --> 05:55:49.090
That's why it's been very pleasing to hear

3558380993
05:55:49.092 --> 05:55:51.196
many members speak about apprenticeships,

3165791670
05:55:51.197 --> 05:55:53.957
which are a perfect example
of this, and I welcome any

2639790339
05:55:53.958 --> 05:55:56.514
ambition to expand opportunities
for young people.

728571746
05:55:56.515 --> 05:55:59.223
But warm words must be
followed by structural change.

1672501882
05:55:59.224 --> 05:56:02.783
University was once the most favoured
destination for economic growth,

1085024051
05:56:02.873 --> 05:56:05.281
but that is economically
out of reach for many.

3907624720
05:56:05.282 --> 05:56:08.781
Still, the journey of apprenticeship
is a renewed ticket to economic

302844983
05:56:08.782 --> 05:56:12.826
growth and to the skilled workforce
this country urgently needs,

959755157
05:56:12.827 --> 05:56:16.974
including engineers,
manufacturers and technicians.

3696754362
05:56:16.975 --> 05:56:19.281
You cannot build frigates
or maintain fighter

4064075289
05:56:19.282 --> 05:56:22.174
jets with a generation left behind.

2752820497
05:56:22.175 --> 05:56:25.586
I quickly want to turn now to
an example that illustrates precisely

1956640874
05:56:25.872 --> 05:56:28.679
what backing businesses ought
to look like in practice,

2158029626
05:56:28.872 --> 05:56:32.775
and where government procurement
could fit in if it chooses to,

3973980770
05:56:32.776 --> 05:56:34.630
to make a transformative difference.

1035529024
05:56:34.631 --> 05:56:37.881
I've spoken to local textile
business owners in Leicester,

4053723650
05:56:37.882 --> 05:56:41.175
Madam Deputy Speaker, the city
that used to clothe the world,

613441002
05:56:41.176 --> 05:56:43.081
the second richest country in Europe,

513258477
05:56:43.082 --> 05:56:45.578
at one stage because of its industry.

2709584317
05:56:45.579 --> 05:56:48.386
Unfortunately, it's on its
knees now because contracts,

2243000023
05:56:48.387 --> 05:56:50.042
instead of being given to young,

2185048304
05:56:50.043 --> 05:56:53.172
hard working British
entrepreneurs, are now given

81699543
05:56:53.173 --> 05:56:55.429
to foreign companies
such as those in China,

1260457535
05:56:56.871 --> 05:57:00.722
awarding defence uniform contracts
to Chinese manufacturers is

3565246667
05:57:00.723 --> 05:57:03.783
simply is not simply an economic
error, but a strategic one.

2393913125
05:57:03.784 --> 05:57:07.726
It creates a supply chain
dependency on foreign nations.

4257770997
05:57:07.727 --> 05:57:09.833
At the precise moment when the government

357085837
05:57:09.834 --> 05:57:12.072
is asking us to take defence seriously.

408212252
05:57:12.073 --> 05:57:14.291
Leicester's textile sector exists.

3627971221
05:57:14.292 --> 05:57:15.444
The capability exists.

1728854430
05:57:15.445 --> 05:57:20.078
The security case for buying
British has never been stronger.

666251080
05:57:20.079 --> 05:57:22.738
The NHS again is the largest
employer in the country

4109663670
05:57:22.739 --> 05:57:25.046
and one of the largest
procurers of textiles,

1759381962
05:57:25.047 --> 05:57:28.371
from uniforms to bedding
and surgical gowns for staff clothing.

1505317549
05:57:28.372 --> 05:57:29.725
The potential is enormous.

2928836910
05:57:29.726 --> 05:57:32.626
A targeted commitment
to NHS procurement from

625620832
05:57:32.628 --> 05:57:34.482
UK manufacturers and from Leicester.

633352150
05:57:34.483 --> 05:57:36.688
Manufacturers in
particular, would not only

1835730867
05:57:36.689 --> 05:57:38.894
support local jobs
and local supply chains,

2173321594
05:57:38.896 --> 05:57:41.954
it would reduce carbon emission
from long distance shipping,

2452991851
05:57:41.955 --> 05:57:43.909
strengthen our supply chain resilience

1774261530
05:57:43.910 --> 05:57:46.472
and build exactly the kind of productive,

876559566
05:57:46.473 --> 05:57:51.126
skilled employment base that
the government says it wants to create.

3581678873
05:57:51.128 --> 05:57:51.679
Thank you.

2952904130
05:57:51.679 --> 05:57:53.672
>> Doctor Peter Prinsley.

2111610775
05:57:53.673 --> 05:57:55.478
>> Thank you, Madam Deputy Speaker.

2687742261
05:57:55.872 --> 05:57:58.179
I'm very grateful to be
making a contribution

1061652475
05:57:58.889 --> 05:58:00.644
for a debate on the King's Speech.

2982936451
05:58:00.646 --> 05:58:02.473
It touches on what, in my view,

1035338927
05:58:02.474 --> 05:58:05.722
is the core foundation
of the nation's future,

2784742931
05:58:05.723 --> 05:58:07.226
which is defensive readiness.

3472384964
05:58:07.227 --> 05:58:09.588
Now, I want to focus my remarks on what

4062127770
05:58:09.589 --> 05:58:12.626
is a real part of our national defence,

2948232018
05:58:12.628 --> 05:58:16.930
and that is the defence of our
democracy and the defence

1736613087
05:58:16.932 --> 05:58:21.076
of our communities from
hostile foreign influence.

1914864767
05:58:21.077 --> 05:58:23.885
Now, you might be forgiven
for thinking that

1462938442
05:58:23.886 --> 05:58:26.323
defence defensive readiness is about

966082933
05:58:26.325 --> 05:58:29.024
the quality of ships
and aircraft and cyber

352645199
05:58:29.025 --> 05:58:32.571
systems and military capabilities,

4113568964
05:58:32.572 --> 05:58:36.473
but it is also whether our
elections are secure,

4253621186
05:58:36.474 --> 05:58:38.479
whether our public debate is protected,

3306483447
05:58:38.831 --> 05:58:40.836
and whether communities in this country

103982734
05:58:40.837 --> 05:58:44.232
can live free from hatred and fear.

1759770490
05:58:44.233 --> 05:58:49.830
Now, make no doubt that foreign
interference is a threat.

1313237732
05:58:49.831 --> 05:58:52.439
The Ryecroft review made
it clear that this country

163178643
05:58:52.440 --> 05:58:54.929
faces a persistent problem
of foreign interests,

317578293
05:58:54.929 --> 05:59:00.378
seeking to exert influence on
and to interfere in our politics.

834771853
05:59:00.379 --> 05:59:04.720
This should be a concern to
every member of this House.

3532574561
05:59:04.721 --> 05:59:07.738
Now, our elections are
the foundations of our democracy.

4238212403
05:59:07.739 --> 05:59:10.625
If hostile states can use
online disinformation

3967764964
05:59:10.626 --> 05:59:13.233
and covert influence to
shape our political debate,

3485747950
05:59:13.233 --> 05:59:15.678
they're attacking
the public's right to decide

2143080856
05:59:15.679 --> 05:59:19.477
the future of this country
freely and fairly.

2673136821
05:59:19.478 --> 05:59:21.786
Now, I am proud that
this government is right

4126032743
05:59:21.786 --> 05:59:23.741
to strengthen political finance rules,

2070626964
05:59:23.876 --> 05:59:27.827
including tighter requirements on
company donations and measures aimed

791199277
05:59:27.828 --> 05:59:32.982
at preventing foreign actors using
companies to influence UK politics.

3120481836
05:59:32.983 --> 05:59:35.885
Some of this is well known.

2906005576
05:59:35.886 --> 05:59:40.037
Millions of pounds from Thailand
and the curious friendship between

3543824790
05:59:40.039 --> 05:59:43.282
the Member for Great Yarmouth
and the world's richest man.

589675058
05:59:49.875 --> 05:59:55.027
The CST, the Community Security Trust
records anti-Semitic activity.

1007586899
05:59:55.028 --> 05:59:58.275
This is now at record levels,

2825291874
05:59:58.276 --> 06:00:00.633
and I did really welcome
the eloquent speeches

292493833
06:00:00.878 --> 06:00:04.839
from the Member for Hemel Hempstead
and the Member for Morley,

3018644591
06:00:04.840 --> 06:00:09.434
who neither of whom are
any longer in their seat.

3198130233
06:00:09.435 --> 06:00:12.927
Now, not every anti-Semitic
incident is foreign directed,

3347278699
06:00:12.928 --> 06:00:16.378
and it is clear that hostile
foreign actors amplify hatred

1013939575
06:00:16.379 --> 06:00:20.682
online and use this to
further divide our society.

794314138
06:00:20.683 --> 06:00:26.233
And that is why the threat from
Iran and the IRGC matters so much.

3747186661
06:00:26.875 --> 06:00:32.376
The security Ministers stated
that the UK has responded

2821258495
06:00:32.376 --> 06:00:35.326
to 20 Iran backed plots
since the start of 2022,

1097274026
06:00:35.327 --> 06:00:37.381
presenting potentially lethal threats to

2688278960
06:00:38.833 --> 06:00:40.738
British citizens and to UK residents.

2943715275
06:00:40.739 --> 06:00:45.225
This clearly presents a foreign
policy and domestic security issue,

709086949
06:00:45.226 --> 06:00:50.932
which I strongly believe this
government must tackle head on.

634178234
06:00:50.933 --> 06:00:55.926
So what can we do to ensure
defensive readiness?

3404692565
06:00:55.927 --> 06:00:58.826
We must ensure strong election security,

2062004496
06:00:58.827 --> 06:01:01.885
strong action against
foreign online interference

648303961
06:01:01.886 --> 06:01:04.840
and indeed robust protection
for Jewish communities

2893633529
06:01:04.842 --> 06:01:07.284
facing real and sustained threats.

395848576
06:01:07.285 --> 06:01:11.027
My constituents and communities
across the country rightly expect

1663923322
06:01:11.028 --> 06:01:15.232
the democracy to be protected
and all their neighbours to be safe.

1635135144
06:01:15.233 --> 06:01:17.876
And there is certainly.

3463152188
06:01:17.878 --> 06:01:18.832
>> I thank my hon.

4115182050
06:01:18.833 --> 06:01:21.927
Friend for taking intervention.

2104688093
06:01:21.928 --> 06:01:25.238
He's making >> A trademark excellent
and well thought out speech,

1731740320
06:01:25.239 --> 06:01:28.000
which >> Is what we come to
expect from in this place.

2342304456
06:01:28.001 --> 06:01:30.584
>> I wonder if he would take a moment,

430356564
06:01:30.585 --> 06:01:33.446
as I know he's a real champion
of the BBC World Service,

2239619881
06:01:33.447 --> 06:01:36.256
just to mention the importance
of the BBC World Service

2254902216
06:01:36.257 --> 06:01:39.066
and the BBC monitoring service
play in that soft power.

1406665579
06:01:39.067 --> 06:01:40.873
That and the defence of our nation.

3632009673
06:01:40.874 --> 06:01:49.429
>> I welcome the Member for Harlow.

165910168
06:01:49.430 --> 06:01:49.882
For his.

1396458814
06:01:49.883 --> 06:01:55.275
I welcome his intervention and I do
agree that the BBC World Service

3227350024
06:01:55.276 --> 06:02:00.057
is almost the best example of
our soft power in this country,

4242499341
06:02:00.058 --> 06:02:03.580
and I welcome the extra
investment that has been promised

2835917805
06:02:03.581 --> 06:02:06.240
by this government to support
the work of the world.

2237284429
06:02:06.241 --> 06:02:08.550
I would very much like
it to be much greater,

3586246173
06:02:08.551 --> 06:02:16.329
and we will do all we can to support
the World Service going forward.

747974026
06:02:16.330 --> 06:02:21.083
So what I have to say is that
this duty that we have to protect

3654221455
06:02:21.084 --> 06:02:26.229
democracy is an absolute
sacred duty of this House.

1339265670
06:02:26.230 --> 06:02:30.436
And I don't think that this
is this is a simple wish,

1265630248
06:02:30.437 --> 06:02:34.786
and I'm sure that this is
something that we can all do.

3284252163
06:02:34.787 --> 06:02:35.339
Thank you.

1221447127
06:02:35.875 --> 06:02:37.679
Sarah Dyke.Â
>> Thank you, Deputy Speaker

2334457925
06:02:37.680 --> 06:02:42.175
I'd like to extend my
condolences to the family,

4070355353
06:02:42.176 --> 06:02:48.476
friends and colleagues of Lance
Bombardier, Ciara O'Sullivan,

2634580817
06:02:48.477 --> 06:02:50.834
who sadly died on Friday
following an incident

4012109523
06:02:50.879 --> 06:02:52.534
at the Royal Windsor Horse Show.

3696650952
06:02:52.535 --> 06:02:56.084
Madam Deputy Speaker, it's
a pleasure to follow the hon.

3019181572
06:02:56.085 --> 06:02:59.638
Member for Bury St Edmunds and Stowmarket

199274024
06:02:59.639 --> 06:03:01.755
and for his powerful speech,

3525894526
06:03:01.756 --> 06:03:05.380
and I'm delighted to
speak in this debate on

3225440056
06:03:05.381 --> 06:03:07.486
the Gracious Speech Madam Deputy Speaker.

2037929222
06:03:07.487 --> 06:03:10.045
Rural Britain is home to
nearly 10 million people.

2597179263
06:03:10.046 --> 06:03:14.032
It produces our food and it is
critical to delivering net zero

3310042778
06:03:14.033 --> 06:03:17.444
and it's host to much of
the infrastructure our defence depends on,

2012386617
06:03:17.445 --> 06:03:19.934
from naval air stations
and training estates,

240394003
06:03:19.935 --> 06:03:23.233
to sonar manufacturers
and helicopter production lines,

4030493837
06:03:23.233 --> 06:03:26.730
to the farms and energy networks
that keep the country running.

2139177829
06:03:26.731 --> 06:03:30.780
Rural Britain is not
a backdrop to national defence,

3599248625
06:03:30.781 --> 06:03:32.086
it is the backbone of it.

2845756379
06:03:32.087 --> 06:03:34.534
Yet the rural economy is nearly 20% less

1457208287
06:03:34.535 --> 06:03:37.232
productive than the national average.

4256802893
06:03:37.233 --> 06:03:40.339
That gap is not and should
not remain inevitable.

1433011252
06:03:40.340 --> 06:03:43.935
It is a product of policy
choices, and those choices matter

1764807085
06:03:43.936 --> 06:03:47.136
for defence readiness as much
as they matter for growth.

1731050825
06:03:47.137 --> 06:03:49.693
Madam Deputy Speaker
Glastonbury and Somerton sits

2430773473
06:03:49.879 --> 06:03:52.436
at the heart of Britain's
defence industrial base.

4061755564
06:03:52.879 --> 06:03:55.187
RNAS Yeovilton HMS Heron
is home to the Fleet

2757106485
06:03:55.188 --> 06:03:57.784
Air ARM's wildcat and commando helicopter

672508951
06:03:57.785 --> 06:04:01.836
force in Templecombe
designs and manufacturers,

3769147052
06:04:01.837 --> 06:04:03.189
designs and manufacturers.

3420192933
06:04:03.190 --> 06:04:05.581
The sonar systems that
are the eyes and ears

1493588336
06:04:05.582 --> 06:04:07.437
of the Royal Navy's submarine fleet,

2244369502
06:04:08.885 --> 06:04:12.383
and was awarded a Â£1.85
billion contract two years

2859021750
06:04:12.384 --> 06:04:15.777
ago to keep doing so for another 15 years.

4052886874
06:04:15.778 --> 06:04:19.784
The constituency is also home to
companies important to the defence

3616416203
06:04:19.785 --> 06:04:23.030
supply chain like needles
and pins Aerospace aerospace,

2449820212
06:04:23.031 --> 06:04:26.084
based in Somerton that
provides precision textile

4228652061
06:04:26.879 --> 06:04:28.783
engineering for aviation and defence.

1311011896
06:04:28.784 --> 06:04:30.831
And just over the border, of course,

3554773473
06:04:30.832 --> 06:04:33.040
in the constituency of
my right and my hon.

810251645
06:04:33.041 --> 06:04:36.930
Friend the Member for Yeovil,
Leonardo Helicopters

4107902055
06:04:36.932 --> 06:04:38.335
employs around 3300 people,

3722064589
06:04:39.838 --> 06:04:41.744
many of whom live in my constituency.

1838446675
06:04:41.745 --> 06:04:46.580
Now, Leonardo is the UK's only end
to end rotary wing manufacturer,

2621587617
06:04:46.581 --> 06:04:49.037
and I welcome the new
medium helicopter contract

1397217250
06:04:49.879 --> 06:04:51.634
that was finally awarded in March.

2503247864
06:04:51.635 --> 06:04:56.481
But the path to that decision should
worry every member of this House.

3771177337
06:04:56.482 --> 06:04:59.946
This is no way to run
a defence industrial strategy.

1660031741
06:04:59.947 --> 06:05:05.140
The Defence Investment Plan
was promised in autumn 2025.

1681291646
06:05:05.141 --> 06:05:08.442
It's now May 2026 and the delay
has created a credibility

2831421058
06:05:08.443 --> 06:05:13.383
issue with industry and with our allies.

3794217002
06:05:13.384 --> 06:05:17.084
Madam Deputy Speaker,
releasing a plan is not

2793233073
06:05:17.085 --> 06:05:19.041
the same as funding or delivering one.

2350708457
06:05:19.042 --> 06:05:22.685
The Liberal Democrats have
been clear this government

1665406840
06:05:22.686 --> 06:05:25.731
must commit to 3% of GDP
on defence by 2030,

275781665
06:05:25.732 --> 06:05:28.179
and we have called for cross-party talks

2241202744
06:05:28.179 --> 06:05:29.836
to agree the route to get there.

671185799
06:05:29.837 --> 06:05:35.379
We have also proposed a Â£20
billion defence bond programme

268085464
06:05:35.380 --> 06:05:38.744
to kick start investment in
the capital intensive assets.

2854759616
06:05:38.745 --> 06:05:43.634
The Strategic Defence Review,
identified because the IFS itself,

3907174444
06:05:43.635 --> 06:05:46.151
suggests that borrowing to invest in

1539138336
06:05:46.152 --> 06:05:48.006
defence can support economic growth,

1258802066
06:05:48.007 --> 06:05:55.183
particularly when spending is
investment heavy and we must restart

1973131303
06:05:55.184 --> 06:06:02.192
negotiations to rejoin
the So British defence firms,

2763107275
06:06:02.193 --> 06:06:06.282
including those in Somerset
and the southwest,

3202607120
06:06:06.283 --> 06:06:09.344
can compete for European
contracts and the UK can play

2730959776
06:06:09.345 --> 06:06:13.483
its full part in collective
European rearmament.

3663936726
06:06:13.485 --> 06:06:17.191
Defence readiness also depends
on how we treat those who serve.

565399891
06:06:17.192 --> 06:06:19.686
And as chair of the Women in Defence APPG,

1126442077
06:06:19.687 --> 06:06:23.033
I believe it is crucial that we see

2716933033
06:06:23.034 --> 06:06:26.980
at least 30% female representation across

882602274
06:06:26.981 --> 06:06:28.585
the defence enterprise by 2030.

1041875410
06:06:28.586 --> 06:06:32.488
Last night we held our summer reception,
which was well attended by hon.

3950003204
06:06:32.489 --> 06:06:36.237
Members and armed forces
in our Armed Forces

3792656668
06:06:36.238 --> 06:06:37.892
and the wider defence community.

2210482934
06:06:37.893 --> 06:06:41.187
Now, in conversation with
the Managing Director of MP aerospace,

2445385590
06:06:41.188 --> 06:06:44.588
I was shocked to learn that
women are 7% more vulnerable

1677932809
06:06:44.589 --> 06:06:47.483
than their male counterparts
on the front line,

3113862200
06:06:47.483 --> 06:06:51.989
simply because they are wearing
body armour that doesn't fit.

4151807191
06:06:51.990 --> 06:06:54.197
The Ministry of Defence
has said they could

2583776706
06:06:54.197 --> 06:06:56.136
deliver new armour plates from 2029,

831859568
06:06:56.137 --> 06:07:01.338
but Banbury Deputy Speaker
this can't come soon enough.

1633642773
06:07:01.339 --> 06:07:03.987
Yeah, we are increasingly at risk.

885521580
06:07:03.988 --> 06:07:07.240
International and geopolitical shocks,

2750706123
06:07:07.241 --> 06:07:09.296
rising prices and food chain disruption.

620518832
06:07:09.297 --> 06:07:11.804
The obvious solution is
to incentivise farmers to

3193272388
06:07:11.885 --> 06:07:14.293
grow enough feed here at
home, you would think.

896192610
06:07:14.294 --> 06:07:16.991
But yet England is
the only country in Europe

2469909011
06:07:16.992 --> 06:07:19.686
that doesn't financially support farmers

3265841076
06:07:19.687 --> 06:07:21.792
to produce food Stymieing food production

2781300968
06:07:21.793 --> 06:07:24.238
and innovation in
the food and drink sector.

1684113411
06:07:24.239 --> 06:07:27.989
The omission of a good food bill
is a massive missed opportunity

2418113663
06:07:27.990 --> 06:07:32.140
to back British farmers,
improve public health.

1441959766
06:07:32.141 --> 06:07:34.640
I won't, I'm afraid, due to time and give

862060644
06:07:34.641 --> 06:07:38.443
our food system the long term framework.

2293637978
06:07:38.444 --> 06:07:39.246
It badly needs.

4273084214
06:07:39.247 --> 06:07:43.183
A national food strategy is
needed now more than ever.

1520039669
06:07:43.184 --> 06:07:46.384
Ignoring the largest British
business sector is simply

166901617
06:07:46.385 --> 06:07:50.534
shortsighted and the rural
economy cannot grow,

1848940147
06:07:50.535 --> 06:07:53.187
whilst its largest sector
is left without a plan.

2447091710
06:07:53.188 --> 06:07:55.093
So to conclude, Madam Deputy Speaker,

261313355
06:07:55.884 --> 06:07:58.492
defence readiness is not
just about the front line,

1536000165
06:07:58.891 --> 06:08:02.835
it's about whether the country
behind the front line is resilient.

4080420142
06:08:02.836 --> 06:08:06.836
Rural England is not a backdrop to
national defence, it is a backbone.

53911392
06:08:06.837 --> 06:08:10.195
So if this government is serious
about defence readiness,

1125165336
06:08:10.196 --> 06:08:13.139
it must be serious about
backing rural Britain,

620799541
06:08:13.140 --> 06:08:15.189
about backing British industry,

2143445746
06:08:15.190 --> 06:08:20.539
about backing the men
and women who serve our country.

288402464
06:08:20.540 --> 06:08:20.991
>> Here.

1255936643
06:08:20.992 --> 06:08:22.887
>> Melanie Ward thank.

3983186282
06:08:22.888 --> 06:08:24.392
>> You, Madam Deputy Speaker.

3150580194
06:08:24.393 --> 06:08:29.986
I rise to speak in this debate in
support of His Majesty's speech.

1052411678
06:08:29.987 --> 06:08:32.597
I rise to to call for our
government to take bolder

4265829373
06:08:32.598 --> 06:08:36.337
action on many of
the challenges that our country,

1997896599
06:08:36.338 --> 06:08:39.146
indeed our world, faces,
the global instability that we

291211108
06:08:39.147 --> 06:08:43.090
are living through is of
a scale not seen for decades.

3119129343
06:08:43.092 --> 06:08:48.635
The power shifts are real now more
than at any time since World War Two.

412169333
06:08:48.636 --> 06:08:52.637
We must stand up and defend our
values on the international stage.

3784018472
06:08:52.638 --> 06:08:55.987
To do that, we need more hard power.

4107162400
06:08:55.988 --> 06:08:56.790
Yes, much more.

1387870492
06:08:56.791 --> 06:09:01.348
But we should protect
and wield our soft power as well.

1182506928
06:09:01.884 --> 06:09:03.489
After 14 years of Tory neglect,

163624882
06:09:03.490 --> 06:09:06.537
our government's commitment
to defence investment

1243845850
06:09:06.539 --> 06:09:08.994
is vital not only to
our national security,

3530380066
06:09:08.995 --> 06:09:12.434
but also to communities like mine.

1832277932
06:09:12.435 --> 06:09:16.836
In Fife, from Â£340 million
invested in Rosyth Dockyard

3705920313
06:09:16.837 --> 06:09:20.386
to support for methyl based Navantia.

2361516581
06:09:20.387 --> 06:09:23.735
Now with 120 new jobs
and 20 new apprenticeships,

1344702966
06:09:23.736 --> 06:09:27.689
this investment is creating skilled
jobs and driving the local economy.

2824050773
06:09:27.690 --> 06:09:31.035
It comes alongside
a new government support

1269498181
06:09:31.036 --> 06:09:33.385
package for defence sector SMEs such

2613471320
06:09:33.386 --> 06:09:38.292
as Viper Applied Sciences in Aberdeen

464723910
06:09:38.293 --> 06:09:40.098
and Power Photonics in Dalgety Bay.

178277767
06:09:40.099 --> 06:09:43.088
UK government backing is
helping to strengthen

3849164517
06:09:43.089 --> 06:09:46.040
our local economy for the future

2999418131
06:09:46.041 --> 06:09:51.789
and after two decades of wilful
neglect by the SNP on defence skills,

189509750
06:09:51.790 --> 06:09:53.494
Fife and Kirkcaldy in particular,

1582586046
06:09:53.495 --> 06:09:56.137
also stands ready to
play our part in rapidly

495867508
06:09:56.138 --> 06:10:01.250
skilling up the next generation of
workers in the defence industry.

3816946603
06:10:01.251 --> 06:10:04.140
We must heed warnings on
the Defence Investment

2972096346
06:10:04.141 --> 06:10:06.047
Plan and rapidly make this a reality,

1085943295
06:10:06.048 --> 06:10:10.301
and I am sure that the Defence
Secretary will agree with that.

3607270651
06:10:10.302 --> 06:10:13.562
And as we strengthen our nation's
ability to protect our people,

1597084302
06:10:13.563 --> 06:10:18.085
we must work with our allies
and form new relationships,

1147860502
06:10:18.086 --> 06:10:22.289
including stronger relations with
our European allies and friends.

3933014001
06:10:23.887 --> 06:10:26.545
Our collective defence is
a cause of utmost urgency,

1768599588
06:10:26.881 --> 06:10:30.437
but so is the defence of our
common values democracy,

207414883
06:10:30.438 --> 06:10:31.943
rule of law and human rights.

2286905746
06:10:31.944 --> 06:10:36.491
Make no mistake, they are under attack.

2284982194
06:10:36.492 --> 06:10:42.333
We must act faster to build the UK's
national resilience to our country,

2413371981
06:10:42.334 --> 06:10:44.392
and our people are not yet ready to face

1044243518
06:10:44.393 --> 06:10:46.491
the kinds of turbulence and crises,

1129278871
06:10:46.492 --> 06:10:50.296
even conflict, that may lie in our future.

3243230076
06:10:50.297 --> 06:10:53.040
Comparable European nations are well ahead

2718427577
06:10:53.041 --> 06:10:55.489
of us in building their resilience,

1660405337
06:10:55.490 --> 06:11:01.292
and it is time to put this work
on turbocharge here in the UK,

708393187
06:11:01.293 --> 06:11:04.191
as we build our hard power
and our resilience,

1574559008
06:11:04.192 --> 06:11:08.296
it would be a mistake to allow
our soft power to fall away.

305056397
06:11:08.297 --> 06:11:08.797
Dartford.

1519622401
06:11:08.798 --> 06:11:12.295
A proud achievement of
the last Labour government

1550692987
06:11:12.296 --> 06:11:15.151
is a body that we miss today.

3076242662
06:11:15.152 --> 06:11:18.190
Amid so much conflict
and global health crises,

3645420785
06:11:18.191 --> 06:11:21.387
like the latest Ebola outbreak.

3316919918
06:11:21.388 --> 06:11:23.043
As defence chief said this week,

2510773270
06:11:23.044 --> 06:11:27.636
recent cuts to the aid Budget are
a source of deep pain to many of us,

1808571772
06:11:27.637 --> 06:11:30.338
but no one more so than the children

3488974401
06:11:30.339 --> 06:11:32.195
going to bed hungry because of them.

700858428
06:11:32.196 --> 06:11:35.797
In north east Nigeria, where
I once served as an aid worker,

3620138071
06:11:35.887 --> 06:11:39.346
more than 1 million people
affected by the conflict,

2387809562
06:11:39.347 --> 06:11:43.094
with Boko Haram risk being cut
off from food and nutrition

541255424
06:11:43.095 --> 06:11:47.190
support because of cuts to
the World Food Programme.

1195382967
06:11:47.191 --> 06:11:50.689
What happens when the world cuts aid?

159129577
06:11:50.690 --> 06:11:54.589
At the time of more global conflict than

3156786684
06:11:54.590 --> 06:11:56.396
any other time since World War Two,

1491063624
06:11:56.883 --> 06:11:59.489
already displaced people
will be further displaced.

1197612750
06:11:59.490 --> 06:12:03.203
That is what they will migrate
in search of survival.

2094908047
06:12:04.887 --> 06:12:06.392
>> Will she give Layla Moran?

2556791040
06:12:06.393 --> 06:12:08.249
I thank my colleague for giving way.

12477375
06:12:08.250 --> 06:12:10.858
She's making an informed
and very well made speech.

2523268116
06:12:10.858 --> 06:12:14.275
Does she agree with me that as we
we need to seek to look to how we

2854246672
06:12:14.276 --> 06:12:17.945
can expand international aid to
deliver for the world's poorest,

3482294316
06:12:17.946 --> 06:12:19.751
but also to regain moral leadership

3439190701
06:12:19.751 --> 06:12:21.911
and a crucial part, as was made by my hon.

3628896575
06:12:21.911 --> 06:12:25.022
Friend and my friend from Harlow,
that the BBC World Service,

312732231
06:12:25.023 --> 06:12:28.139
where those those frequencies
have been taken over

99647917
06:12:28.140 --> 06:12:30.445
by Russian and other
anti-democratic nations,

4045165128
06:12:30.446 --> 06:12:32.403
must be a key part in supporting that,

773506129
06:12:32.404 --> 06:12:34.392
not just in the future, but right now.

3398045181
06:12:34.393 --> 06:12:34.945
>> My hon.

1918871905
06:12:34.946 --> 06:12:38.399
Friend makes an excellent point
about the importance of soft power

737004394
06:12:38.400 --> 06:12:41.644
and why it is such an important
complement to hard power.

928171664
06:12:41.644 --> 06:12:44.153
Madam Deputy Speaker, it
has become common to say

1820142650
06:12:44.154 --> 06:12:46.639
that the rules based
order is dead or dying,

2811088715
06:12:46.640 --> 06:12:51.391
but we must stand with our
allies to preserve and defend

1731405728
06:12:51.392 --> 06:12:55.295
all that was built to
protect humanity from evil.

3632945986
06:12:55.296 --> 06:12:58.340
In the ashes of two world
wars and the Cold War,

2938247192
06:12:58.342 --> 06:12:59.746
data shows that since 2012,

3498403901
06:12:59.884 --> 06:13:03.690
there has been an increase in
the number of countries where

250627556
06:13:03.691 --> 06:13:06.990
mass atrocity crimes are
occurring and action is needed.

125843459
06:13:06.991 --> 06:13:12.001
Let us remind ourselves we are
talking about genocide, war crimes,

70272097
06:13:12.001 --> 06:13:14.891
ethnic cleansing,
and crimes against humanity.

3397197092
06:13:14.892 --> 06:13:19.244
From Sudan to Sinjar, the most
heinous crimes that exist,

3582776481
06:13:20.887 --> 06:13:22.390
mass identity based violence.

4043011134
06:13:22.391 --> 06:13:25.394
Where is the UK government's
strategy to work

2514205127
06:13:25.394 --> 06:13:28.245
with like minded countries
to prevent this?

1049569036
06:13:28.246 --> 06:13:29.098
There isn't one.

3976950960
06:13:29.099 --> 06:13:31.141
We need to change that and fast,

4286626129
06:13:31.142 --> 06:13:34.140
and doing so would be
an obvious complement to

1427303149
06:13:34.141 --> 06:13:36.447
the important work that
the Foreign Secretary

1608649611
06:13:36.447 --> 06:13:39.197
is doing on women and girls in Sudan,

3626660792
06:13:39.197 --> 06:13:44.688
the United Nations and
the International Criminal Court,

2728575834
06:13:44.689 --> 06:13:48.148
two imperfect but vital institutions
designed to protect and respond

2301829521
06:13:48.149 --> 06:13:50.857
to humanity at its worst are
under enormous pressure,

4102884898
06:13:50.858 --> 06:13:53.892
not least from the US
government, whose sanctions

1847027070
06:13:53.893 --> 06:13:56.840
are designed to hobble the ICC.

2881294051
06:13:56.840 --> 06:13:59.901
Our government is supporting
the UN and the ICC,

872736622
06:13:59.902 --> 06:14:03.649
but we should be making the case
for them loudly and globally,

1898599279
06:14:03.650 --> 06:14:06.643
and working with like
minded allies to protect

231963085
06:14:06.644 --> 06:14:09.953
and defend their very existence.

519368686
06:14:09.954 --> 06:14:14.491
And it's time to act at
the pace required by global events.

3333961786
06:14:14.492 --> 06:14:17.499
The time for incremental
micro-steps is over.

3453500496
06:14:17.500 --> 06:14:19.943
We must act at a scale appropriate to

188263292
06:14:19.944 --> 06:14:22.090
the urgency of the moment we are in.

1027028416
06:14:22.092 --> 06:14:25.794
On Iran, the government is doing
the right thing on Ukraine.

326099576
06:14:25.795 --> 06:14:28.241
The government is doing the right thing.

1659109758
06:14:28.242 --> 06:14:29.746
But in Palestine and Lebanon,

939535774
06:14:29.747 --> 06:14:33.797
the world can see for
itself what is happening.

3423876432
06:14:33.798 --> 06:14:36.743
World experts say there has
been genocide in Gaza.

3577216901
06:14:36.744 --> 06:14:39.652
Israel continues to bomb and kill doctors,

1224760769
06:14:39.653 --> 06:14:43.546
hospitals and aid workers
in Gaza and Lebanon.

645055840
06:14:43.547 --> 06:14:46.506
Israeli settlers in the West
Bank are trying to ethnically

4278281839
06:14:46.894 --> 06:14:50.492
cleanse Palestinians with
the support of their government.

940560202
06:14:50.493 --> 06:14:50.894
I will.

3474389743
06:14:50.894 --> 06:14:52.550
>> Madam Deputy Speaker, my hon.

2507942127
06:14:52.894 --> 06:14:55.802
Friend is making a really
thought provoking contribution,

2557119503
06:14:55.803 --> 06:14:58.463
and I also thank her for her
leadership in this area

301852898
06:14:58.464 --> 06:15:01.072
of international aid before
she came to this place.

2784513140
06:15:01.072 --> 06:15:02.529
And now, while she is in it,

892679005
06:15:02.530 --> 06:15:06.342
will she agree with me that
with Gaza specifically in mind,

993031473
06:15:06.343 --> 06:15:08.801
as the cameras have turned
away, that we cannot.

3433975848
06:15:08.802 --> 06:15:11.491
And as a British and UK Labour government,

2015065866
06:15:11.492 --> 06:15:13.648
we have a moral responsibility to continue

372432951
06:15:13.649 --> 06:15:15.603
to provide whatever medical assistance

1146481562
06:15:15.604 --> 06:15:19.696
and expertise is required in that area.

2600842006
06:15:19.697 --> 06:15:20.249
>> My hon.

3923785372
06:15:20.250 --> 06:15:22.797
Friend is absolutely
right, and as a doctor,

2113826958
06:15:22.798 --> 06:15:26.141
I know how much he understands
and feels this and the need

2383342196
06:15:26.142 --> 06:15:29.138
for the world to do better
and make change in this

1591207585
06:15:29.139 --> 06:15:33.295
area and stop just talking
about making change.

3963889284
06:15:33.296 --> 06:15:36.592
It is time for a much bolder
action from our government to

3189467290
06:15:36.593 --> 06:15:40.102
stand against what is happening
and to influence events.

642948678
06:15:40.103 --> 06:15:43.291
Not more words, but more action.

2498190982
06:15:43.292 --> 06:15:46.549
Comprehensive sanctions on Israeli
officials who are responsible

3107155175
06:15:46.550 --> 06:15:50.844
for human rights violations
and denial of aid,

2016096200
06:15:50.845 --> 06:15:53.993
a ban on settlement trade
and outlawing British

1953163950
06:15:53.994 --> 06:15:56.693
charities from funnelling
money to settlements.

2252249556
06:15:56.694 --> 06:15:58.903
To start with, it is
not good enough to say

790667669
06:15:58.904 --> 06:16:00.961
that it is difficult to do these things.

1504690007
06:16:01.891 --> 06:16:03.998
Civilians need us to act and both history

4086131691
06:16:03.999 --> 06:16:07.446
and the public are judging us now.

2914647749
06:16:07.447 --> 06:16:10.355
Madam Deputy Speaker, incremental
change does not cut it.

2612915046
06:16:10.356 --> 06:16:12.446
In this time of massive global shifts,

1654945409
06:16:12.447 --> 06:16:15.843
we must be bold in our global action,

2916281027
06:16:15.844 --> 06:16:17.501
just as we must be here at home.

3604995120
06:16:18.892 --> 06:16:19.845
>> >> Paul Kohler.

3352149947
06:16:19.846 --> 06:16:21.340
Thank you, Madam Speaker.

3547717679
06:16:21.342 --> 06:16:23.849
And can I congratulate
the Member for Cowdenbeath

2783314946
06:16:23.850 --> 06:16:27.996
and Kirkcaldy on her passionate
and compassionate speech.

138766974
06:16:27.997 --> 06:16:31.647
There is much in the King's Speech
I can support in principle,

195506831
06:16:31.648 --> 06:16:34.644
and we on these benches
will engage constructively

2180807904
06:16:34.644 --> 06:16:38.503
but not uncritically with its proposals.

636796414
06:16:38.504 --> 06:16:40.858
Too often, however, this
government's instinct

2307052379
06:16:40.860 --> 06:16:43.117
has been to prevaricate
rather than to lead,

1379079387
06:16:43.118 --> 06:16:45.776
and nowhere is that more
apparent than its dithering

2958524324
06:16:45.777 --> 06:16:47.542
over our relationship with Europe.

3204034043
06:16:47.543 --> 06:16:51.340
Any measure that rebuilds even a fraction

2210521192
06:16:51.342 --> 06:16:53.447
of what the Member for Clacton undermined

1183837796
06:16:53.448 --> 06:16:55.503
and the Conservatives demolished deserve

3545764885
06:16:55.504 --> 06:16:58.295
supportÂ in the most narrow terms

3508536401
06:16:58.296 --> 06:17:01.898
I welcome the European Partnership
Bill, but let us be candid.

2444766013
06:17:01.899 --> 06:17:05.304
The government is not
proposing an ambitious reset.

2626120447
06:17:05.304 --> 06:17:09.603
This is a best tinkering, not
the full bodied re-engagement

3231085051
06:17:09.604 --> 06:17:11.408
that our economy desperately needs.

2700519106
06:17:11.409 --> 06:17:12.993
And the public are demanding.

1954827730
06:17:12.994 --> 06:17:16.546
The debate on this issue is
too often conducted as though

574617682
06:17:16.547 --> 06:17:20.998
opinion froze a decade ago,
but the country has moved on,

2150375467
06:17:20.999 --> 06:17:23.206
with two thirds of
the public now favouring

4055805341
06:17:23.207 --> 06:17:26.245
proper re-engagement with the EU.

2358576923
06:17:26.246 --> 06:17:29.194
Sadly, the current Prime
Minister has tied himself

1279200930
06:17:29.195 --> 06:17:31.989
down with red lines that
make that impossible,

3465508989
06:17:31.990 --> 06:17:35.007
whilst the leading contender
to take over from him

2347301323
06:17:35.008 --> 06:17:37.651
has already U-turned
on his EU commitments,

3802321148
06:17:37.652 --> 06:17:41.541
along with his U-turns on proportional

2150028759
06:17:41.542 --> 06:17:43.396
representation and the fiscal rules,

3231926634
06:17:43.397 --> 06:17:49.801
Andy Burnham doesn't just turn and U-turn,

4119574577
06:17:49.802 --> 06:17:51.407
he spins the National Bureau of

1515961182
06:17:51.408 --> 06:17:55.492
Economic Research estimates that Brexit

3667217620
06:17:55.493 --> 06:17:57.250
has reduced UK GDP by at least 6%,

402082887
06:17:57.251 --> 06:18:00.692
with business investment running
nearly 20% lower than comparable

3734104111
06:18:00.693 --> 06:18:05.411
economies and both employment
and productivity down roughly 4%.

1929695956
06:18:05.412 --> 06:18:09.510
That is why I'm urging every Labour
MP who wants to grow our economy

2937629464
06:18:09.892 --> 06:18:13.642
and properly fund our armed
services to vote for our amendment,

3068029333
06:18:13.643 --> 06:18:17.346
which simply calls on
their government to begin

3992574360
06:18:17.347 --> 06:18:21.291
negotiating a new customs
union with the EU.

416104445
06:18:21.292 --> 06:18:23.498
The world today bears
little resemblance to

3314691005
06:18:23.899 --> 06:18:25.855
the one in which Brexit was conceived.

3892561737
06:18:25.856 --> 06:18:29.300
Putin's Russia is four years
into a land war in Europe,

3844814223
06:18:29.301 --> 06:18:32.251
has sent warships into
British waters and poisoned

421711980
06:18:32.894 --> 06:18:34.599
British citizens on British soil.

3060401907
06:18:34.600 --> 06:18:39.201
Whilst NATO is under threat from
an American president who treats

1845337818
06:18:39.202 --> 06:18:43.197
collective security as a transaction
rather than a commitment.

3998153746
06:18:43.198 --> 06:18:46.247
The case for building our
European partnerships,

55538093
06:18:46.248 --> 06:18:50.148
rather than forsaking them,
has never been stronger.

1975916675
06:18:50.149 --> 06:18:54.801
The new UK, EU Security and Defence
Partnership is consequently welcome,

880419492
06:18:55.896 --> 06:18:58.653
but aspiration must be matched
with urgent commitment.

3105066452
06:18:58.654 --> 06:19:02.347
The threats gathering on our
continent will not wait

3290208717
06:19:02.348 --> 06:19:05.549
until Labour indulges
in another psychodrama,

1267297264
06:19:05.550 --> 06:19:08.408
like the ones that plagued
the previous Tory government.

374013539
06:19:08.409 --> 06:19:11.197
The proposal to deepen
cooperation with Europol,

1391190594
06:19:11.197 --> 06:19:15.310
Frontex and the European
Migration Network to combat

2375621560
06:19:15.311 --> 06:19:18.947
people smuggling are overdue and welcome,

4227674036
06:19:18.947 --> 06:19:20.451
while sharing biometric data,

396946593
06:19:20.894 --> 06:19:23.100
criminal records
and intelligence on people

3608378202
06:19:23.101 --> 06:19:29.295
smuggling gangs should never have
ended, notwithstanding Brexit.

2215597991
06:19:29.296 --> 06:19:30.651
But we need to go further.

891193621
06:19:30.652 --> 06:19:34.553
The EU is transitioning to a new
migration asylum pact and we,

193627126
06:19:34.894 --> 06:19:38.504
like other non-EU countries
including Norway and Switzerland,

3606089774
06:19:38.505 --> 06:19:40.510
should be involved in that arrangement.

2942847151
06:19:40.894 --> 06:19:43.150
As my party's Northern
Ireland spokesperson,

3109156754
06:19:43.151 --> 06:19:45.507
I welcome the bill's
provisions on simplifying

487450645
06:19:45.508 --> 06:19:49.792
food and plant movements between
Great Britain and Northern Ireland.

1014719202
06:19:49.793 --> 06:19:52.701
But let's not pretend
the Windsor framework is delivered.

3585482233
06:19:52.702 --> 06:19:55.847
The frictionless utopia that was promised.

3192665051
06:19:55.848 --> 06:19:59.251
Despite the purported benefits
of the green lane Mid Sussex,

847523752
06:19:59.251 --> 06:20:03.398
nearly 60% of businesses
report challenges,

528370810
06:20:03.399 --> 06:20:06.399
and one 1 in 3 have ceased
trading with the GB entirely.

3725158928
06:20:06.400 --> 06:20:11.241
The tensions come from the fact Northern
Ireland has advantage of access

1619136742
06:20:11.242 --> 06:20:14.405
to EU single market or the rest
of the UK does not, of course,

1628158450
06:20:14.406 --> 06:20:17.849
and the only durable way to manage
the complications that arise is

2593549788
06:20:17.850 --> 06:20:22.096
to bring the rest of the UK into
closer alignment with the EU.

3434025369
06:20:22.097 --> 06:20:26.096
Finally, I'd like to turn to
the conservative amendment.

1103256732
06:20:26.097 --> 06:20:29.759
Whilst we support the need to increase
defence spending and join them in

1448505399
06:20:29.760 --> 06:20:33.751
calling for urgent publication of
the delayed Defence Investment Plan,

3086820748
06:20:33.751 --> 06:20:37.108
their cynical attempt amendment
fails to reference the Tories

3843925719
06:20:37.108 --> 06:20:40.608
own responsibility for
the hollowing out of the armed forces,

455159016
06:20:40.610 --> 06:20:44.155
whilst their call to abandon
the remedial order remedying

2964536229
06:20:44.892 --> 06:20:46.898
defects in the Tories flawed Legacy Act

594877769
06:20:47.896 --> 06:20:50.301
disingenuously implies
that veterans who served

1727853361
06:20:50.302 --> 06:20:52.557
in Northern Ireland are
currently protected,

2190881037
06:20:52.558 --> 06:20:55.650
protected from prosecution,
despite the fact that

3436500436
06:20:55.651 --> 06:20:58.259
the provisions in that act
purported to confer such

2620132898
06:20:58.260 --> 06:21:02.251
immunity were never brought into
force and were subsequently

1068343837
06:21:02.253 --> 06:21:04.058
declared unlawful by the UK courts.

3723272734
06:21:04.059 --> 06:21:07.608
So an ending can I ask the House
to please vote for our amendment,

437639544
06:21:09.855 --> 06:21:11.358
but not the conservative one?

739646218
06:21:11.360 --> 06:21:11.911
Thank you.

860516903
06:21:11.911 --> 06:21:15.397
>> Victoria Collins thank
you, Madam Deputy Speaker.

2072201761
06:21:15.398 --> 06:21:18.457
During the last King's Speech,
I delivered my maiden speech.

1886208544
06:21:18.458 --> 06:21:21.718
In the two years since then,
the world has changed dramatically.

2232524102
06:21:21.719 --> 06:21:24.149
The global insecurity we
face was always real.

1824869721
06:21:24.150 --> 06:21:26.558
But now that insecurity
has come to our shores,

2563276677
06:21:26.559 --> 06:21:27.863
it's felt in our economy,

3855503727
06:21:27.864 --> 06:21:32.796
in our homes, in our everyday lives,
living in a global tinderbox.

159378645
06:21:32.797 --> 06:21:35.204
And the voters have spoken
the local elections,

3456366875
06:21:35.205 --> 06:21:37.613
they sent a clear message
that they don't trust

1847755088
06:21:37.614 --> 06:21:40.120
the current government to
defend their interests,

1740104503
06:21:40.121 --> 06:21:42.577
to create that resilience,
stability and growth,

148926601
06:21:42.578 --> 06:21:46.951
which is key to our defence
as a nation in Harpenden,

685646295
06:21:46.952 --> 06:21:49.400
Berkhamstead, Tring and our villages,

2962881606
06:21:49.401 --> 06:21:51.506
families feel that instability every day,

236514056
06:21:51.507 --> 06:21:53.463
with many struggling to pay the bills,

3048768544
06:21:53.464 --> 06:21:57.125
wondering how they're going to pay
the fluctuating mortgage or the rent.

2237680693
06:21:57.126 --> 06:22:00.487
They see the high cost of childcare
and worry about their children

2786459921
06:22:00.488 --> 06:22:03.095
getting the right education
or staying safe online,

1783857368
06:22:03.096 --> 06:22:04.801
all while costs continue to rise,

2499678734
06:22:04.802 --> 06:22:07.057
with parents like Louisa
from Wheathampstead

4209839297
06:22:07.058 --> 06:22:09.866
worried about getting their
kids into the right school,

3669085451
06:22:09.867 --> 06:22:11.973
her child has already been through failed

1716414538
06:22:11.974 --> 06:22:13.778
placements with specific Sen needs,

3425347857
06:22:13.779 --> 06:22:17.140
and she said it's only the specialist
school where they feel safe,

2922701198
06:22:17.141 --> 06:22:18.495
settled and able to learn.

61770624
06:22:18.496 --> 06:22:21.455
And then the younger generation
look at this broken system

4188989344
06:22:21.456 --> 06:22:24.416
and no wonder they question
whether it's even pay into it.

2053246478
06:22:24.417 --> 06:22:28.077
Hannah, a sixth former from Harpenden,
says I've never considered living

1940237578
06:22:28.078 --> 06:22:31.590
here in the future because it's too
expensive to buy a place to live,

2937868322
06:22:31.592 --> 06:22:35.052
and the new build homes are nowhere
near being genuinely affordable.

1924116735
06:22:35.053 --> 06:22:38.013
At over half a million by even
by the official definition,

2654105549
06:22:38.014 --> 06:22:40.622
the older generation worked
hard and they paid into

4119561190
06:22:40.623 --> 06:22:43.407
the system have not got back
what they were promised.

3528450109
06:22:43.408 --> 06:22:46.316
One of my local constituents
said I started work at 15

3816935168
06:22:46.896 --> 06:22:50.250
and the deal was that I would
end at finish working at 60.

2674018557
06:22:50.251 --> 06:22:53.510
But then another said I've struggled
with poverty and exhaustion

3128464461
06:22:53.511 --> 06:22:57.100
and been told to carry on
working until I was 66.

167000151
06:22:57.101 --> 06:23:00.204
I've been plagued with
health issues ever since,

3607523378
06:23:00.205 --> 06:23:02.661
and then the young
and middle aged professionals

2836799562
06:23:02.662 --> 06:23:04.067
are squeezed in the middle.

1571647871
06:23:04.068 --> 06:23:07.178
The path laid out before them
has shifted beneath their feet.

3950230557
06:23:07.179 --> 06:23:09.186
They were told by the house, have kids.

4234106055
06:23:09.187 --> 06:23:11.497
If you want to work in
the job that you love,

1025011182
06:23:11.498 --> 06:23:14.608
and you'd have more wealth
and freedom than your parents did.

3422628916
06:23:14.608 --> 06:23:16.765
But each generation now faces less wealth,

2978477244
06:23:16.766 --> 06:23:18.519
less freedom, fewer opportunities.

3588291032
06:23:18.899 --> 06:23:21.508
And no wonder politics is
being turned on its head,

3728569388
06:23:21.509 --> 06:23:25.851
all while they scroll through
a picture perfect world that

2062730766
06:23:25.852 --> 06:23:28.701
falls apart at every news
headline that comes out.

1785315261
06:23:28.702 --> 06:23:31.911
The businesses in our communities,
the backbone of our economy,

3743910119
06:23:31.911 --> 06:23:34.970
are finding it harder, more
expensive, and more challenging.

2285347678
06:23:34.971 --> 06:23:37.228
Darren, who runs fair
at 190 in Berkhamsted,

4091053839
06:23:37.229 --> 06:23:39.686
a serial entrepreneur who
knows what he's doing,

2257425307
06:23:39.687 --> 06:23:43.154
is finding the costs
and burdens unsustainable.

1552230827
06:23:43.155 --> 06:23:47.550
He says that the continuing rise in
staff costs is killing this sector,

1797163870
06:23:47.551 --> 06:23:50.300
and goes on to say
the government is driving

3679116491
06:23:50.301 --> 06:23:51.903
experienced entrepreneurs away,

1386098990
06:23:51.904 --> 06:23:55.655
quietly draining the UK of the people most

3629022837
06:23:55.656 --> 06:23:58.448
likely to build higher and invest again.

416798652
06:23:58.450 --> 06:24:00.555
Our communities feel again and again that

2070630154
06:24:00.557 --> 06:24:02.555
they are done too, not worked with.

661970533
06:24:02.557 --> 06:24:05.917
And there's no greater example than
the top down development plans

4098798989
06:24:05.918 --> 06:24:09.075
that are completely undemocratic
and bypass local communities.

1597669280
06:24:09.076 --> 06:24:11.534
They understand the need
for housing, but not on

2861760395
06:24:11.535 --> 06:24:14.392
the scale that the infrastructure
locally cannot handle.

1692941231
06:24:14.393 --> 06:24:17.102
Lucy, from Tring, like many,
share a genuine alert on

1336149772
06:24:17.103 --> 06:24:19.610
the impact of our communities
and our landscapes.

429398475
06:24:19.611 --> 06:24:22.119
Liz, from Redbourn says
the legacy of this Labour

1328881648
06:24:22.120 --> 06:24:24.477
government will see
the death of our villages,

3688002319
06:24:24.478 --> 06:24:28.202
the effect of wildlife on wildlife
and chalk streams would be immense.

2633197572
06:24:28.203 --> 06:24:32.161
So for our communities, for our
country, the time for action is now.

1789520486
06:24:32.161 --> 06:24:34.669
This King's Speech could
have been an opportunity

1463640339
06:24:34.670 --> 06:24:36.754
to reset the direction of this country.

1025750866
06:24:36.755 --> 06:24:40.467
Although I welcome tackling energy
costs and sewage and ending

2788000420
06:24:40.468 --> 06:24:44.496
the unfair residential leaseholds,
they don't go far enough.

1224268433
06:24:44.497 --> 06:24:47.407
Where is the urgent action to
end the social care crisis?

1542061074
06:24:47.408 --> 06:24:50.148
Where is the good Food bill
to back British farmers?

1223137284
06:24:50.149 --> 06:24:55.007
Where's the commitment to spending
3% of GDP on defence by 2030?

372361726
06:24:55.008 --> 06:24:57.759
That vital part to keep our borders safe?

2435186679
06:24:57.760 --> 06:25:00.575
Where is this digital sovereign strategy?

2826385082
06:25:00.576 --> 06:25:02.655
Where is the Defence Readiness Bill

2448600544
06:25:02.656 --> 06:25:05.501
and where is the ambitious EU reset Bill?

283600731
06:25:05.501 --> 06:25:08.254
We need desperately to grow our economy

1252547
06:25:08.255 --> 06:25:10.159
something to empower our communities,

2275331337
06:25:10.160 --> 06:25:11.804
make us richer and safer.

1494800147
06:25:11.805 --> 06:25:14.514
This country is at a crossroads.

3175375369
06:25:14.515 --> 06:25:16.569
Our current government isn't delivering.

195147015
06:25:16.570 --> 06:25:18.275
The two old parties are finished.

1801065996
06:25:18.276 --> 06:25:21.034
The populists and extremists
want to burn things down.

3742874315
06:25:21.035 --> 06:25:22.639
Millions of people want change.

1279864091
06:25:22.640 --> 06:25:24.345
That is about building things up.

3508413080
06:25:24.346 --> 06:25:26.604
And this is the kind of
positive change that

1271326050
06:25:26.605 --> 06:25:28.409
the Liberal Democrats are offering.

2455534893
06:25:28.410 --> 06:25:31.668
Change that brings people, communities
and our country together,

769392641
06:25:31.899 --> 06:25:36.851
ready to face that international
insecurity that rocks our borders.

2494412935
06:25:36.852 --> 06:25:39.661
We believe in better, stronger trade,

1947131008
06:25:39.662 --> 06:25:42.309
defence and defence
relationship with Europe,

2281344628
06:25:42.310 --> 06:25:44.165
one that truly delivers for Britain.

3102188945
06:25:44.166 --> 06:25:46.371
I believe in collaborative
sovereignty that

4154497510
06:25:46.372 --> 06:25:49.656
values our resilience through prosperity,

4092706914
06:25:49.657 --> 06:25:51.554
production and partnership.

3741293607
06:25:51.554 --> 06:25:53.559
Backing British domestic strength while

589998968
06:25:53.560 --> 06:25:55.566
working with our allies to be stronger,

2633997446
06:25:55.567 --> 06:25:57.470
whether through military sovereignty,

3386092107
06:25:57.471 --> 06:26:00.577
digital sovereignty, energy
sovereignty and food sovereignty.

2596390834
06:26:00.578 --> 06:26:04.749
But being stronger as a nation to be
stronger partners internationally.

2986849251
06:26:04.750 --> 06:26:07.714
As politicians, we must
turn up again and again.

84233085
06:26:07.715 --> 06:26:09.572
We have to turn up in the messiness,

954352135
06:26:09.572 --> 06:26:11.731
but be honest about what needs to be done.

2346285777
06:26:11.732 --> 06:26:13.036
And with that comes hope.

552400818
06:26:13.036 --> 06:26:15.644
Hope for a better future
for growth and prosperity.

3827511595
06:26:15.646 --> 06:26:16.851
And so the time is now.

1513047032
06:26:16.907 --> 06:26:19.566
The moment for us to be
radically reasonable is now.

1362175894
06:26:19.567 --> 06:26:22.603
It's time that the system
worked for local people.

782552889
06:26:22.604 --> 06:26:24.712
And just as I closed in my maiden speech,

2744737648
06:26:24.905 --> 06:26:28.467
I shared that my mother came to this
country in search of opportunity.

2004436667
06:26:28.468 --> 06:26:30.424
And through everything that I do here,

1649189417
06:26:30.425 --> 06:26:34.608
I want to ensure that same opportunity
is available for all who seek it.

596229328
06:26:34.610 --> 06:26:37.086
And so, Madam Deputy Speaker,

3736335976
06:26:37.087 --> 06:26:39.595
that means a bolder vision
for our Great Britain.

814747153
06:26:39.596 --> 06:26:41.051
And that needs to start now.

258008897
06:26:42.903 --> 06:26:43.605
>> Thank you.

1607836198
06:26:43.606 --> 06:26:47.558
>> >> Deputy Speaker And can
I start by acknowledging

930543641
06:26:47.559 --> 06:26:49.866
the dedication to public
service of all those

1577222970
06:26:49.867 --> 06:26:52.458
who serve or have served
or support those in our

2768548553
06:26:52.459 --> 06:26:56.105
armed forces and our
wider defence industry?

2872600429
06:26:56.106 --> 06:26:59.064
There are opportunities, as
well as glaring omissions from

3032127373
06:26:59.065 --> 06:27:01.773
what the government has put
forward for this session.

3861697507
06:27:01.774 --> 06:27:04.682
I'm certainly glad to see new
legislation coming forwards

644155739
06:27:04.683 --> 06:27:08.311
in two of the biggest issues
facing us in North Norfolk,

2307264359
06:27:08.312 --> 06:27:10.570
getting our NHS back on
its feet and getting

3020159379
06:27:10.903 --> 06:27:12.659
sewage out of our rivers and seas.

2885176265
06:27:12.660 --> 06:27:14.817
I hope the forthcoming health Bill will be

2410146906
06:27:14.818 --> 06:27:16.873
another step towards rebuilding our NHS.

939329374
06:27:16.874 --> 06:27:20.482
After the appalling damage done by
successive conservative governments.

239790043
06:27:20.483 --> 06:27:22.893
I'm keen to see how
the Bill can tackle some of

3440786278
06:27:22.894 --> 06:27:25.351
the rural inequalities we
face in North Norfolk,

3341912706
06:27:25.352 --> 06:27:27.708
though, which aren't just
about health access,

564908533
06:27:27.709 --> 06:27:29.513
they're also about health outcomes,

3214187587
06:27:29.514 --> 06:27:32.675
and it's one reason we will not
back down over Benjamin Court,

1823991811
06:27:32.676 --> 06:27:36.135
a vital rehabilitation resource for
people leaving hospital that was

2511464515
06:27:36.136 --> 06:27:39.294
closed down by Norfolk County
Council under the Conservatives.

3352770728
06:27:39.295 --> 06:27:39.845
Elsewhere.

1443228163
06:27:39.846 --> 06:27:42.956
I'm pleased that the clean Water
Bill will be coming forward,

32807211
06:27:42.957 --> 06:27:46.621
but I do have serious worries that it
will be yet another piece of weak,

2875458599
06:27:46.622 --> 06:27:49.178
watered down legislation
that doesn't place proper

348327063
06:27:49.179 --> 06:27:51.586
pain on water companies
when they behave badly.

1457632377
06:27:51.587 --> 06:27:54.758
I've been delighted that our
years of campaigning have helped

2328072803
06:27:54.759 --> 06:27:57.467
secure Â£ 83 million of
investment from Anglian Water,

106253231
06:27:57.468 --> 06:27:59.724
which has already brought
down sewage spills

3870885176
06:27:59.725 --> 06:28:01.682
by 95% in some parts of north Norfolk.

2513270263
06:28:01.683 --> 06:28:04.313
But there is still much
to do and I won't rest

1850545455
06:28:04.314 --> 06:28:06.572
until sewage spills are
a thing of the past.

2245192920
06:28:06.572 --> 06:28:08.679
The government should also ensure that it

1241327250
06:28:08.679 --> 06:28:10.636
takes steps to make our chalk streams,

1686550682
06:28:10.637 --> 06:28:13.444
Unesco Natural Heritage sites
and recognise and protect

959741539
06:28:13.445 --> 06:28:16.203
the unique character of chalk
streams like the Glaven,

4239959042
06:28:16.204 --> 06:28:18.658
the Stiffkey and
the Bura in North Norfolk.

508190873
06:28:18.659 --> 06:28:22.509
Moving on, the forthcoming education
for All Bill will be cautiously

3259330643
06:28:22.510 --> 06:28:26.064
welcomed by parents of children
with SEND in Our area.

1628590746
06:28:26.065 --> 06:28:30.353
It recognises that the system is
broken and that it's failing.

1437459934
06:28:30.354 --> 06:28:34.408
Schools, local authorities, parents
and, most significantly, children.

1564750077
06:28:34.409 --> 06:28:36.715
But many parents have
told me they're worried

1864733438
06:28:36.717 --> 06:28:38.809
about how the rights of their children

3096861200
06:28:38.810 --> 06:28:41.017
will be affected
and how access to adequate

847269432
06:28:41.018 --> 06:28:42.873
support will be guaranteed for them.

1413354072
06:28:42.907 --> 06:28:45.768
The bill also needs to make
sure that reform of the Send

427259236
06:28:45.769 --> 06:28:48.658
system ensures equal access
for the whole country,

1707710057
06:28:48.659 --> 06:28:50.764
and ends the continuing postcode lottery.

3856761411
06:28:50.765 --> 06:28:54.009
I've heard concerns from
constituents about how underserved

1308965012
06:28:54.010 --> 06:28:56.759
some of our coastal communities are,

2367145046
06:28:56.760 --> 06:28:59.159
and how far young people
have to travel just

1690536719
06:28:59.160 --> 06:29:01.368
to get to a setting
that suits their needs.

4048329715
06:29:01.369 --> 06:29:04.227
I've also spoken to parents
with primary school children

668859081
06:29:04.228 --> 06:29:06.685
who are worried about
what's happening for them.

394537829
06:29:06.686 --> 06:29:08.691
Right now in our overstretched schools,

2828815620
06:29:08.692 --> 06:29:11.050
they worry that these
reforms will be too late

2254644288
06:29:11.051 --> 06:29:13.308
for hundreds of send
children who need help.

600187783
06:29:13.309 --> 06:29:13.559
Now.

930885849
06:29:13.909 --> 06:29:17.889
I'm also awaiting the Digital Access
to Services bill with interest.

3464224958
06:29:17.890 --> 06:29:20.799
The government missed a lot
of opportunities, in my view,

3785267365
06:29:20.800 --> 06:29:22.805
with last year's data bill to legislate

3166315145
06:29:22.807 --> 06:29:24.562
for a more data driven government,

4176916644
06:29:24.563 --> 06:29:27.269
a government that's better
at doing things digitally.

1029612810
06:29:27.271 --> 06:29:30.130
Part of this is actually about
ensuring people who don't

3619699950
06:29:30.131 --> 06:29:32.787
do things digitally can still
access those services.

3669723806
06:29:32.789 --> 06:29:35.799
And yet, just weeks after
assuring me on the bill committee

2511513820
06:29:35.800 --> 06:29:38.005
that existing legislation
would cover this,

1115011004
06:29:38.006 --> 06:29:40.764
they announced their ill fated
digital ID pet project.

272101743
06:29:40.765 --> 06:29:43.673
So despite believing that
digital transformation is a key

2190717947
06:29:43.674 --> 06:29:46.231
ingredient to fixing what's
broken in our country,

1428425176
06:29:46.232 --> 06:29:48.742
I will be pushing them
again, as I did last year,

3900769280
06:29:48.743 --> 06:29:51.567
to enshrine in law a right
to non-digital ID to protect

828995256
06:29:51.568 --> 06:29:55.358
the elderly and vulnerable
people in North Norfolk,

3621861469
06:29:55.358 --> 06:29:57.467
or those who simply don't want to use it.

3752035497
06:29:57.468 --> 06:29:59.071
There are still, frustratingly,

4158239035
06:29:59.072 --> 06:30:02.311
some important omissions from the 35 bills

2785337301
06:30:02.312 --> 06:30:04.117
put before us on defence readiness.

4160427127
06:30:04.118 --> 06:30:06.926
I'm disappointed to see no
concrete action on financial

940305354
06:30:06.927 --> 06:30:09.031
transparency in the overseas territories.

595834966
06:30:09.032 --> 06:30:11.809
Madam Deputy Speaker offshore
tax havens are simply

4072299648
06:30:11.810 --> 06:30:14.854
hiding places for dirty
money, oligarchs, wealth,

2076520176
06:30:14.855 --> 06:30:17.911
rogue states and corporations
dodging their responsibilities

878917587
06:30:17.911 --> 06:30:20.161
while ordinary people pick up the bill.

1698331642
06:30:20.162 --> 06:30:23.725
We know these gaps can be closed,
so why isn't the government prepared

913632253
06:30:23.726 --> 06:30:27.161
to bring forward legislation to
close them once and for all?

1850970765
06:30:27.162 --> 06:30:30.408
Meanwhile, many young people
are worried about how

3640622010
06:30:30.409 --> 06:30:33.458
their careers will be
impacted by by AI and older,

1207942436
06:30:33.459 --> 06:30:36.608
vulnerable people are
worried about how criminals

424462068
06:30:36.608 --> 06:30:39.207
can misuse AI to defraud and scam them.

3407049237
06:30:39.208 --> 06:30:40.965
We have to keep up with the times.

1731709133
06:30:40.965 --> 06:30:43.776
We have to ensure that AI is
providing benefits to all,

1499592864
06:30:43.777 --> 06:30:45.933
not just concentrating wealth and power in

549104344
06:30:45.934 --> 06:30:48.169
the hands of a few select tech Barons.

3942468994
06:30:48.170 --> 06:30:52.367
In foreign states, the economy used
to be powered mainly by people.

65842118
06:30:52.904 --> 06:30:55.209
Increasingly, it's being
powered by software,

3105888389
06:30:55.210 --> 06:30:57.665
and therefore it's
increasingly regrettable that

2704312497
06:30:57.666 --> 06:31:00.274
The King's Speech didn't
make provision to begin to

832153702
06:31:00.275 --> 06:31:02.482
adapt the tax base to
accommodate the hyper

744365166
06:31:02.483 --> 06:31:04.588
concentration of ownership of tech firms,

966089495
06:31:04.589 --> 06:31:07.647
starting with the digital services
tax Madam Deputy Speaker.

3004134794
06:31:07.648 --> 06:31:10.509
It was clear to me from
the thousands of doors I knocked

4012226757
06:31:10.510 --> 06:31:13.320
on over the course of
the local elections and the many,

3880405655
06:31:13.321 --> 06:31:15.176
many emails I'm receiving every day,

3557094282
06:31:15.177 --> 06:31:17.133
that change is not coming fast enough.

4255889753
06:31:17.134 --> 06:31:19.590
People feel the government
is dragging its feet,

2905094871
06:31:19.592 --> 06:31:21.398
that the machinery of the state has

692151999
06:31:21.399 --> 06:31:23.353
little interest in actually delivering

1378604872
06:31:23.354 --> 06:31:25.309
the radical change this country needs.

2712761431
06:31:25.310 --> 06:31:27.316
There are green shoots in the programme

3954036714
06:31:27.317 --> 06:31:29.272
from this government, but little more.

813305971
06:31:29.273 --> 06:31:32.632
I and my Liberal Democrat colleagues
look forward to scrutinising,

2810313110
06:31:32.633 --> 06:31:34.688
pushing and challenging government to do

721281802
06:31:34.689 --> 06:31:36.595
more over the course of this session.

2167389211
06:31:36.596 --> 06:31:37.298
>> Thank you.

2337481416
06:31:37.299 --> 06:31:40.009
>> Madam Deputy Speaker.

1350832751
06:31:40.010 --> 06:31:42.861
Today we've been talking
about defence readiness,

3452301168
06:31:42.862 --> 06:31:47.361
and I commend those members of
the armed forces and indeed,

3746235630
06:31:47.362 --> 06:31:50.311
veterans who live or in
based in my constituency

3132624683
06:31:50.312 --> 06:31:52.357
of Melksham and Devizes.

3942055491
06:31:52.358 --> 06:31:58.114
But, Madam Deputy Speaker, our
defence comes in various forms.

2000716037
06:31:58.115 --> 06:32:01.963
Farming and food security were not
mentioned in the King's Speech,

1664513443
06:32:01.964 --> 06:32:06.160
and this was surely a major omission.

2983082904
06:32:06.161 --> 06:32:10.073
Madam Deputy Speaker, today I'm
wearing a WaterAid tie that I was

3583502796
06:32:10.075 --> 06:32:16.407
given 35 years ago when I started
working with them in Tanzania.

3758663330
06:32:16.408 --> 06:32:18.366
Aid is a major part of our soft power.

2889428039
06:32:19.912 --> 06:32:22.021
It not only helps to save lives and helps

2770970395
06:32:22.907 --> 06:32:24.560
people withstand climate change,

3510939531
06:32:24.561 --> 06:32:28.317
it allows us to stand
tall for all the good

2267272060
06:32:28.318 --> 06:32:30.813
things that we do around the world.

1705466832
06:32:30.814 --> 06:32:35.260
And I'd be grateful if
the Ministers can confirm that

3565477920
06:32:35.261 --> 06:32:40.170
the UK aid will not be
cut further to just 0.1%

2178498597
06:32:40.171 --> 06:32:44.855
of GNI, this is doubly important now that

2079293919
06:32:44.856 --> 06:32:50.761
the spectre of Ebola is haunting Africa.

1154910258
06:32:50.762 --> 06:32:51.313
Thank you.

2458066672
06:32:51.314 --> 06:32:53.922
>> Which brings us to
the front bench contribution.

759616946
06:32:53.923 --> 06:32:57.509
Shadow Ministers David Reed.

1628915089
06:32:57.510 --> 06:33:01.417
>> Thank you, Madam Deputy Speaker,
and it's an honour to wind up

738054543
06:33:01.418 --> 06:33:03.956
the final debate on the King's Speech

3609159748
06:33:03.957 --> 06:33:05.761
for His Majesty's loyal opposition.

1632384918
06:33:05.867 --> 06:33:07.972
We have heard many sterling contributions

380399491
06:33:07.973 --> 06:33:09.577
from members across this House,

3592543397
06:33:09.578 --> 06:33:12.064
and I will turn to some of those shortly.

1423897510
06:33:12.065 --> 06:33:15.616
But I want to first pose once
more the central question of

847328909
06:33:15.617 --> 06:33:20.918
this debate and ask every
member to answer it honestly.

924740519
06:33:20.919 --> 06:33:25.414
Is our national defence truly ready?

2442258499
06:33:25.415 --> 06:33:30.868
Madam Deputy Speaker, my honest
assessment is no, no it is not.

2481454249
06:33:30.869 --> 06:33:33.468
War is no longer a matter of history.

3758966817
06:33:33.469 --> 06:33:38.469
The international order which we
have all lived under is fracturing.

304594126
06:33:38.911 --> 06:33:41.719
War has broken out across
multiple continents and rapid

106615512
06:33:41.720 --> 06:33:44.073
technological advancement
and the accelerating

3399564838
06:33:44.075 --> 06:33:46.429
consequences of climate
change are compounding

465774085
06:33:47.916 --> 06:33:49.569
an already dangerous volatility.

3699717201
06:33:49.570 --> 06:33:51.314
The world is not as it was,

1293126237
06:33:51.315 --> 06:33:55.812
and we cannot afford to
govern as though it is now.

4062475041
06:33:55.813 --> 06:33:58.516
While it's encouraging
that so many members are

4064344488
06:33:58.517 --> 06:34:01.258
engaging with this epoch defining issue,

3690929756
06:34:01.259 --> 06:34:03.567
it is equally clear that
there is a corrosive

3451949681
06:34:03.910 --> 06:34:06.166
complacency at the heart
of this government.

1597626895
06:34:06.167 --> 06:34:09.174
And those are not my words,
Madam Deputy Speaker.

1130804397
06:34:09.175 --> 06:34:12.017
They belong to Lord
Robertson, a former Labour

1088498723
06:34:12.018 --> 06:34:14.715
defence secretary
and former NATO secretary

782952210
06:34:14.715 --> 06:34:17.173
general and one of
the most distinguished voices

3405164709
06:34:17.174 --> 06:34:20.613
in this country's defence establishments.

4196361656
06:34:20.614 --> 06:34:23.866
He did not use them lightly,
and he directed them squarely

3038927590
06:34:23.867 --> 06:34:27.414
at this Prime Minister
and this Chancellor.

2975054306
06:34:27.415 --> 06:34:29.572
When a man of that stature speaks in those

2162863909
06:34:29.573 --> 06:34:32.962
terms about his own party's governments,

3998927728
06:34:32.963 --> 06:34:34.769
this House would do well to listen.

2281467952
06:34:35.911 --> 06:34:39.222
More than that, Madam Deputy
Speaker, there should be no politics

3137941909
06:34:39.223 --> 06:34:42.717
in acknowledging the reality that
stares us plainly in the face.

3152204926
06:34:42.718 --> 06:34:48.461
Where the politics begins legitimately
is in the harder questions,

1507949520
06:34:48.462 --> 06:34:54.217
where the money comes from and how
and what we choose to spend it on.

1615914326
06:34:54.218 --> 06:34:57.767
Turning to the contributions
that we've had opening

2877062994
06:34:57.768 --> 06:35:00.727
the batting was the chair of
the Defence Select Committee.

129304436
06:35:00.728 --> 06:35:04.767
I think we can all agree that he made
quite a brave and powerful speech,

3083708146
06:35:04.768 --> 06:35:06.975
and laid bare the holes
in the government's

2669880830
06:35:06.976 --> 06:35:09.132
approach to defence in a constructive way,

3544635349
06:35:09.868 --> 06:35:13.666
and I've seen him do that
repeatedly as his work as chair,

794051541
06:35:13.667 --> 06:35:17.015
and it was good to see him
wearing his rcds tie as well.

2912334441
06:35:17.016 --> 06:35:18.321
The rise of my right hon.

1430306157
06:35:18.911 --> 06:35:23.864
Friend the Member for Chingford
and Woodford Green, as to be expected,

476906256
06:35:23.865 --> 06:35:26.674
made a excellent speech
and touched on the supply chain

1374589682
06:35:26.675 --> 06:35:29.415
issues that we're seeing
and reliance on China.

2417798154
06:35:29.416 --> 06:35:33.366
Points that I'll come back
to later in my remarks.

2076498232
06:35:33.367 --> 06:35:34.119
The right hon.

2662360790
06:35:35.911 --> 06:35:37.164
Member for Ilford North.

2831091939
06:35:37.165 --> 06:35:41.063
He is no longer here,
but it was quite intimidating

1795679474
06:35:41.064 --> 06:35:46.715
ï¼king seeing the Praetorian
Guard in full force.

3649572636
06:35:46.717 --> 06:35:49.968
He articulated the weighty
issues we face as a country,

23783409
06:35:49.969 --> 06:35:53.018
and I seriously do hope
that defence issues are

1522502670
06:35:53.019 --> 06:35:57.917
front and centre of his
coup d'Ã©tat attempts.

2335940050
06:35:57.918 --> 06:35:58.620
My right hon.

539067713
06:35:59.920 --> 06:36:04.418
Friend the Member for South for South
West Wiltshire illustrated lessons

763535269
06:36:04.419 --> 06:36:08.321
from World War Two and what we need
to learn and act on without delay.

119362017
06:36:08.869 --> 06:36:11.126
Points that were reinforced
by my right hon.

498608443
06:36:12.911 --> 06:36:14.516
Friend for New Forest, the hon.

2895874029
06:36:14.517 --> 06:36:16.462
Member for Newcastle upon Tyne.

1515241620
06:36:16.463 --> 06:36:19.813
I think we can all agree
that she's doing a fantastic

3418575544
06:36:19.814 --> 06:36:22.022
job as trade envoy to
Italy called out some

1476587627
06:36:22.023 --> 06:36:24.331
of the supply chains
that she's seeing in her

576921022
06:36:24.332 --> 06:36:26.489
work at the moment with Italy around GCap,

3428702372
06:36:29.911 --> 06:36:32.417
and pointed out
the government's dither regarding

871441069
06:36:32.911 --> 06:36:35.368
the slow release of
the Defence investment plan.

3863919418
06:36:35.369 --> 06:36:38.177
We've also had other strong
contributions from the hon.

887968174
06:36:38.178 --> 06:36:41.762
Member for Liverpool, West
Derby for Tunbridge Wells,

2682044753
06:36:41.763 --> 06:36:43.367
for Southend East and Rochford.

2449009672
06:36:43.368 --> 06:36:44.464
My right hon.

3088483769
06:36:44.465 --> 06:36:48.315
Friend for Wetherby and Easingwold,
for The Wrekin and for Gosport.

2764171405
06:36:48.316 --> 06:36:48.767
The hon.

3090849291
06:36:48.768 --> 06:36:51.374
Member for Hemel Hempstead,
for Wolverhampton West.

4053558256
06:36:51.375 --> 06:36:52.176
For Cheltenham.

1832217057
06:36:52.911 --> 06:36:56.868
For Leeds South West and Morley
Dunfermline and Dollar and my hon.

2243423784
06:36:56.869 --> 06:37:00.025
Friends for South Shropshire
and South West Devon.

276327640
06:37:00.026 --> 06:37:01.278
Many more contributions.

3649369533
06:37:01.279 --> 06:37:03.435
Too many to mention, Madam Deputy Speaker,

3440039043
06:37:03.436 --> 06:37:06.123
but it was great to see
so many of my constituency

1493473304
06:37:06.866 --> 06:37:09.474
neighbours from the South
West and as the Ministers

2297169090
06:37:09.916 --> 06:37:11.719
opposite has championed repeatedly,

4170456691
06:37:11.720 --> 06:37:14.029
it is a region that will
play a decisive role

4212652089
06:37:14.030 --> 06:37:17.167
in our defence readiness going forward.

1395426974
06:37:17.168 --> 06:37:20.174
Now, Madam Deputy Speaker,
like many in this House,

3463165340
06:37:20.175 --> 06:37:22.617
I am utterly tired, if not bored,

1626346506
06:37:22.618 --> 06:37:26.667
of asking when the Defence Investment
plan will be published and I'm not

4229030013
06:37:26.668 --> 06:37:31.715
even going to bother asking about
the plan Defence readiness Bill.

3330562201
06:37:31.717 --> 06:37:35.465
The government set their own deadline
last autumn and ten months on,

1271893273
06:37:35.467 --> 06:37:41.172
it's still nowhere to be seen now
for the large prime contractors,

441581879
06:37:41.173 --> 06:37:42.764
those too big to fail.

1251582354
06:37:42.765 --> 06:37:46.419
The calculation is simple
they leverage their workforce

991565549
06:37:46.420 --> 06:37:49.369
and industrial base to force
the government's hand.

902460875
06:37:49.370 --> 06:37:51.727
But for smaller companies
in the supply chain,

3366692385
06:37:51.728 --> 06:37:54.366
the picture is far bleaker,

2206588568
06:37:54.367 --> 06:37:57.365
with a meagre number of
contracts being awarded.

4247710930
06:37:57.366 --> 06:37:59.524
They are being starved of work and if they

3225655977
06:37:59.525 --> 06:38:01.429
haven't already gone out of business,

108966146
06:38:01.430 --> 06:38:03.386
many are reaching the same conclusion.

1467378774
06:38:03.387 --> 06:38:06.620
If you want to grow, you have
to go. And go they will.

1654331109
06:38:06.621 --> 06:38:09.278
Madam Deputy Speaker,
the United States and European

3235200805
06:38:09.279 --> 06:38:12.616
defence markets are rising to the moment,

3599503889
06:38:12.617 --> 06:38:17.619
and companies and finance
will follow the business.

4083696745
06:38:17.620 --> 06:38:20.076
The government's indecision
and delay is placing

4279931513
06:38:20.077 --> 06:38:22.184
British defence at the back of the queue,

1778567795
06:38:22.185 --> 06:38:26.671
at precisely the moment when
the queue has never mattered more.

311702695
06:38:26.672 --> 06:38:29.118
This leads me to challenge a phrase used

394023511
06:38:29.119 --> 06:38:33.464
too freely by defence Ministers,

1411705625
06:38:33.465 --> 06:38:34.566
sovereign capability.

1675056909
06:38:34.567 --> 06:38:37.621
For many of the areas that
we most want to excel,

326736919
06:38:37.622 --> 06:38:39.467
true sovereignty is a myth.

1450975894
06:38:39.468 --> 06:38:40.970
Take artificial intelligence.

4046860168
06:38:40.971 --> 06:38:44.168
The best AI needs the best chips.

3189369379
06:38:44.169 --> 06:38:46.666
We do not own the means to production.

945991526
06:38:46.667 --> 06:38:51.218
Our options are either our
American allies or China.

4083137154
06:38:51.219 --> 06:38:54.171
Madam Deputy Speaker,
I know which one I choose.

2860023070
06:38:54.172 --> 06:38:54.822
Take drones.

2287148038
06:38:54.823 --> 06:38:57.972
The government talks a good
game, but most small aerial

2071059216
06:38:57.973 --> 06:39:01.769
drones systems depend
on neodymium magnets,

1421630700
06:39:01.771 --> 06:39:04.273
and China controls over
90% of global supply.

4060109575
06:39:04.274 --> 06:39:07.977
That's not a supply chain problem.

1233040692
06:39:07.978 --> 06:39:09.581
It's a strategic vulnerability.

996058422
06:39:09.915 --> 06:39:13.575
What's truly in our national interest
is to identify these dependencies,

1179548349
06:39:13.576 --> 06:39:16.836
a point reinforced by the chair
of the Defence Select Committee.

862586980
06:39:16.837 --> 06:39:19.547
I know this has work that
his committee is looking at

2772022429
06:39:19.548 --> 06:39:22.616
and swiftly partnered with allies
who can help address them.

3550918682
06:39:22.617 --> 06:39:26.866
I do not see that joined up work
happening across government.

3809471016
06:39:26.867 --> 06:39:32.320
That leads me to the structure of
our public defence establishments.

1617399000
06:39:32.321 --> 06:39:36.480
We have roughly 55,000 Ministry
of Defence civil servants,

3340192904
06:39:36.869 --> 06:39:38.875
and yet we recently struggled to deploy

519130582
06:39:38.876 --> 06:39:41.031
a single partially functional destroyer to

846478787
06:39:41.032 --> 06:39:43.469
protect our sovereign base area in Cyprus,

1981450238
06:39:43.470 --> 06:39:47.272
a point that was expanded on by
the Member for Tunbridge Wells.

141730454
06:39:47.915 --> 06:39:51.576
Now, there are many fantastic civil
servants in the Ministry of Defence,

199332998
06:39:51.577 --> 06:39:53.482
and I've had the privilege personally

4230385351
06:39:53.483 --> 06:39:55.289
to work alongside a number of them.

27544668
06:39:55.290 --> 06:39:57.247
But I cannot believe that I'm alone in

2080088367
06:39:57.248 --> 06:40:00.329
seeing the imbalance in that equation.

1772340069
06:40:00.330 --> 06:40:03.868
Lastly, Madam Deputy Speaker, I turn to

2480786291
06:40:03.869 --> 06:40:05.822
our service personnel and veterans. At

1535182716
06:40:05.918 --> 06:40:08.976
every UK training establishment
the law of armed conflict is

727941428
06:40:08.977 --> 06:40:12.669
rigorously instilled into every
recruits and officer cadets,

367229960
06:40:12.670 --> 06:40:15.870
and that legal framework
underpins a service person's

3204231875
06:40:15.871 --> 06:40:19.073
conduct throughout their
career and on operations.

4251115213
06:40:19.075 --> 06:40:22.523
And I speak with the lived
experience as a former Royal Marine,

109984561
06:40:22.524 --> 06:40:24.779
where someone transgresses
from those rules,

1162495032
06:40:24.915 --> 06:40:27.071
they are investigated and if found guilty,

3022065461
06:40:27.072 --> 06:40:32.517
the full weight of the law is
brought to bear, and rightly so.

337754804
06:40:32.518 --> 06:40:36.067
However, the government must
confront an uncomfortable truth by

1889121326
06:40:36.068 --> 06:40:39.730
dragging veterans through
the courts decades after the events,

3893945450
06:40:39.731 --> 06:40:41.937
as will likely occur
under the Government's

4095069398
06:40:41.938 --> 06:40:44.021
Northern Ireland Troubles legislation,

1718828202
06:40:44.022 --> 06:40:48.523
the process becomes the punishment.

4201121555
06:40:48.524 --> 06:40:52.165
Indefinite legal jeopardy,
with no discernible end,

4086377156
06:40:52.166 --> 06:40:54.422
cause a profound
and lasting mental anguish.

1595131402
06:40:54.915 --> 06:40:58.419
And when we apply that same
logic to serving personnel

3928102828
06:40:58.420 --> 06:41:01.620
operating in unimaginably
violent environments,

67172587
06:41:01.621 --> 06:41:04.467
hesitation in the heat of
battle born of legal fear

1941007934
06:41:04.468 --> 06:41:08.476
rather than military
judgements, can cost lives.

2205389331
06:41:08.477 --> 06:41:09.983
For most of us in this House,

2726674317
06:41:09.983 --> 06:41:12.641
it's impossible to truly
comprehend what that means.

2346299636
06:41:13.911 --> 06:41:16.171
But we must try, and we
owe it to the people

1130661646
06:41:16.172 --> 06:41:17.776
that place themselves in harm's

2542840348
06:41:17.777 --> 06:41:20.035
way on our behalf to
give them the assurance

2845216501
06:41:20.036 --> 06:41:21.641
that this House has their back.

1340516531
06:41:21.921 --> 06:41:25.420
Madam Deputy Speaker, in
conclusion, I want to extend

756898229
06:41:25.421 --> 06:41:28.971
the hand of cooperation to
the government and olive

3674937762
06:41:28.972 --> 06:41:31.329
branch offered by
the Leader of the Opposition

357855345
06:41:31.330 --> 06:41:34.415
and carelessly dismissed
by the Prime Minister.

1658465286
06:41:34.416 --> 06:41:37.522
In this new era of
geopolitical instability,

3189996892
06:41:37.523 --> 06:41:39.381
we on this side of the House want to

3701068691
06:41:39.382 --> 06:41:41.236
support the government in delivering

2215660952
06:41:41.237 --> 06:41:43.572
the defence readiness
this country deserves.

2262636506
06:41:43.573 --> 06:41:44.226
Now, my hon.

2990670896
06:41:44.227 --> 06:41:47.025
Friend the Shadow Secretary
of State for defence

2398305670
06:41:47.026 --> 06:41:49.723
has set out conservative
proposals clearly,

3241366959
06:41:49.724 --> 06:41:51.631
and we will continue to work on that,

3413183405
06:41:51.632 --> 06:41:54.375
and I hope the government
will receive them

3807768658
06:41:54.376 --> 06:41:57.620
in the spirit in which they are intended.

3232042759
06:41:57.621 --> 06:42:01.219
Madam Deputy Speaker, our country needs

2518202566
06:42:01.220 --> 06:42:03.226
politicians who can rise to the moment.

4246422545
06:42:03.227 --> 06:42:05.721
This is that moment.

2689283629
06:42:05.722 --> 06:42:07.577
And with that, Madam Deputy Speaker,

2513313007
06:42:07.578 --> 06:42:10.186
I wish the government
Godspeed in this new session,

633754321
06:42:10.187 --> 06:42:12.997
for it is not their party's
fortune that depends on it,

1022203468
06:42:12.998 --> 06:42:14.351
but our nation's security.

595450104
06:42:14.352 --> 06:42:17.219
>> Hear, hear.

1506862174
06:42:17.220 --> 06:42:21.527
>> Before I call the Secretary of
State and I appreciate I am preaching

2027090865
06:42:21.528 --> 06:42:25.326
to the choir because every member
present is indeed present.

3283135791
06:42:25.327 --> 06:42:27.626
But perhaps the message could go back

71342550
06:42:27.628 --> 06:42:29.822
to colleagues who are not that page

2075834731
06:42:29.822 --> 06:42:32.672
four of the Guide to Chamber
Courtesies indicates that.

1511153805
06:42:32.673 --> 06:42:33.174
Have you.

1139637786
06:42:33.175 --> 06:42:42.420
If you have contributed to the debate,
you must return for wind ups.

3552278444
06:42:42.421 --> 06:42:43.423
Secretary of State.

2915268448
06:42:43.424 --> 06:42:45.229
>> Thank you, Madam Deputy Speaker.

3290321143
06:42:45.230 --> 06:42:49.673
>> Can I begin by Paying tribute
to Lance Bombardier Chiara

3616728735
06:42:49.674 --> 06:42:52.723
Sullivan of the King's Troop
Royal Horse Artillery,

2611409196
06:42:52.724 --> 06:42:58.075
who tragically died at
the Windsor Horse Show.

1451236920
06:42:58.076 --> 06:43:00.189
She was a brilliant young soldier,

749493981
06:43:00.190 --> 06:43:02.620
and her commanding officer described her

2048065600
06:43:02.621 --> 06:43:04.476
as a fearless and gifted horsewoman.

142005927
06:43:04.920 --> 06:43:09.832
And I know the thoughts of the whole
house will be with her family

1950210073
06:43:09.833 --> 06:43:14.126
and her comrades as they
come to terms with her loss.

2719914386
06:43:14.126 --> 06:43:18.322
Can I also start by paying
tribute to our armed Forces

2029179205
06:43:18.323 --> 06:43:21.671
personnel for their
professionalism, their dedication.

2019741537
06:43:21.672 --> 06:43:26.176
Because right now we have servicemen
and women keeping us safe

330546034
