a vision for Defending Britain,

3026921021
07:07:20.269 --> 07:07:22.494
making it safer and more secure at home.

3546632984
07:07:22.495 --> 07:07:26.556
I told the House then that we would
step up our support for Ukraine.

4242334423
07:07:26.557 --> 07:07:30.594
We have provided more military
assistance than ever before.

4159478167
07:07:30.595 --> 07:07:34.745
We took on the leadership
of the Ukraine Defence

1825019787
07:07:34.746 --> 07:07:36.551
Contact Group to support the fight.

3707756269
07:07:36.552 --> 07:07:39.009
Today we have established
and lead the coalition

3115601882
07:07:39.010 --> 07:07:41.418
of the willing for Ukraine
to secure the peace.

2349865986
07:07:41.939 --> 07:07:42.439
Tomorrow.

1907684418
07:07:42.440 --> 07:07:45.493
I pledged a new UK Germany
defence agreement.

2020689762
07:07:45.494 --> 07:07:46.948
Less than four months later.

1888115474
07:07:46.949 --> 07:07:49.851
I signed that with Defence
Ministers Pistorius

4260102580
07:07:49.852 --> 07:07:52.145
in the Trinity House agreement

3512990427
07:07:52.146 --> 07:07:55.902
and went on to sign deals with
France, with Norway, with Turkey.

2877073125
07:07:55.903 --> 07:08:02.397
And in that debate, I raised
the scourge of dreadful military housing.

2240371873
07:08:02.398 --> 07:08:07.399
We went on within months to bring
back into public ownership 36,000

1187156601
07:08:07.400 --> 07:08:11.257
homes that our military families live in.

3861970033
07:08:11.258 --> 07:08:14.346
We have upgraded the worst
1000 before last Christmas,

872475053
07:08:14.347 --> 07:08:17.899
and already done another 250 since.

4186065078
07:08:17.900 --> 07:08:23.246
And I said the morale of our service
personnel then was at a record low.

1396090569
07:08:23.247 --> 07:08:27.949
We since then awarded them the biggest
pay rise for nearly two decades.

1458039312
07:08:27.950 --> 07:08:31.913
Extended free childcare
legislated for the first ever

612898639
07:08:31.914 --> 07:08:36.049
Armed Forces Commissioner
to improve service life.

1585640998
07:08:36.050 --> 07:08:37.406
And I say to my right hon.

1308057761
07:08:38.906 --> 07:08:41.314
Friend the Member for
Ilford North, I miss him.

1845050223
07:08:41.315 --> 07:08:45.505
At Cabinet this week, he
gave us a reflective speech.

2407268724
07:08:46.947 --> 07:08:49.253
He's rightly proud of
the government's record

4055214908
07:08:49.254 --> 07:08:51.651
on rebuilding and reforming the NHS,

3179578905
07:08:51.652 --> 07:08:57.858
but I trust he'll agree like he would
argue in defence in in the NHS.

158692375
07:08:57.859 --> 07:08:59.967
I trust he would agree that in defence we

1194199411
07:09:01.947 --> 07:09:03.952
have certainly not been treading water.

1577876635
07:09:03.953 --> 07:09:05.758
Let me close, Madam Deputy Speaker,

3955686098
07:09:05.759 --> 07:09:09.509
