Majesty the King last week.

4044012193
07:09:09.510 --> 07:09:14.303
An increasingly dangerous
and volatile world threatens the UK.

3351542574
07:09:14.947 --> 07:09:16.852
Every element of the nation's energy,

161564451
07:09:16.853 --> 07:09:20.647
