out in what appears to be agony.

2321290497
08:03:38.268 --> 08:03:41.358
After Israel's interception of the global

849516173
08:03:41.359 --> 08:03:44.100
summit flotilla in international waters.

3811716388
08:03:44.101 --> 08:03:46.607
Madam Deputy Speaker, these
were ordinary people,

2793424607
08:03:46.608 --> 08:03:50.454
ordinary people carrying
aid to the starving

2809183293
08:03:50.455 --> 08:03:52.109
and besieged population of Gaza,

1495619177
08:03:52.110 --> 08:03:55.859
their crime refusing to
sit back while the world

821905482
08:03:55.860 --> 08:03:59.858
watches genocide unfold
live on our screens.

718903472
08:03:59.859 --> 08:04:02.359
I met members of this flotilla team here

3399833973
08:04:02.360 --> 08:04:04.064
in Parliament before they sailed.

2002794902
08:04:04.065 --> 08:04:08.470
They were sincere, courageous
people, driven to act because

3555282634
08:04:08.471 --> 08:04:11.409
governments would not move
by images of genocide.

2196196402
08:04:11.410 --> 08:04:12.363
They chose to act.

1812115859
08:04:16.004 --> 08:04:17.759
All 14 British nationals on board.

3553380650
