3973600956
08:22:04.231 --> 08:22:06.188
They say their answer to that is link.

3674755844
08:22:06.189 --> 08:22:08.788
And yet the rules seem
to say that market towns

1686257915
08:22:08.789 --> 08:22:11.576
with that huge hinterland that they also

140858116
