if those are the rules,

1159444163
08:22:20.078 --> 08:22:21.482
those rules need to change?

3933540842
08:22:21.483 --> 08:22:22.535
>> Yeah, absolutely.

829119038
08:22:22.536 --> 08:22:23.136
Absolutely.

4034193863
08:22:23.137 --> 08:22:26.599
And if we can turn to the
the inadequacies of the current framework,

2840439793
