1285733584
08:22:29.131 --> 08:22:32.138
Current criteria includes
the number of remaining branches,

3046383063
08:22:32.139 --> 08:22:34.395
the population size,
the retail centre size,

3885879210
08:22:34.396 --> 08:22:37.705
