4293239442
08:22:49.996 --> 08:22:52.200
Transport distance,
public transport links,

657295642
08:22:52.201 --> 08:22:54.355
population vulnerability and existing cash

3079948182
08:22:54.356 --> 08:22:56.462
services are also all considered by link.

2201696090
08:22:56.463 --> 08:22:58.469
It is, however, the lack of flexibility

4196724260
08:22:58.470 --> 08:23:00.426
of those criteria that is the problem,

2032021650
08:23:00.427 --> 08:23:02.434
